【前言】两个帝国的对望

https://fenxiao.xiaoe-tech.com/#/try_page/1/appkHUDlT435887/a_5c9219dec9dd1_DJvWtWDD

<p><span style="font-size: 14px;"><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;">如果历史上没有秦汉与罗马，世界将会怎样？</span></strong><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;"></span></strong></span></p><p><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;">两千多年前，在欧亚大陆的东西两端出现了两个强大的国家：秦汉和罗马。它们代表着当时古代世界文明的最高辉煌成就。</span></p><p><span style="font-size: 14px;">&nbsp;</span></p><p><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;">英国著名历史学家汤因比在其《历史研究》一书中进行文明比较研究时，提出世界文明发展的两种主要模式，即希腊模式与中国模式。在他看来，古罗马文明是希腊模式高度发展的必然结果，所谓希腊文明亦可称为希腊—罗马文明，而中国的秦汉王朝则是中国模式的开始。</span></p><p><span style="font-size: 14px;">&nbsp;<img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appkHUDlT435887/image/ueditor/28035300_1538622915.jpg" title=".jpg" alt="幻灯片1.JPG"/></span></p><p><br/></p><p><span style="font-size: 14px;"><strong><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体;">这是一门欢迎碰撞，启发你思考的历史课</span></strong><strong><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体;"></span></strong></span></p><p><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;">《秦汉与罗马》专辑结合博物馆文物研究和遗址考古等热点，梳理对照两大文明政治、经济、文化及衣食住行生活的方方面面，不仅关注创造历史的大人物，更关心历史长河中的小人物等各阶层的生活。兼顾历史知识的架构和普及、艺术的审美及博物馆游学旅行的参考指南等功能。</span></p><p><span style="font-size: 14px;">&nbsp;<img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appkHUDlT435887/image/ueditor/21884400_1538622744.jpg" title=".jpg" alt="1 (2).JPG" style="font-size: 14px; white-space: normal;"/></span></p><p><span style="font-size: 14px;"><br/></span></p><p><span style="font-size: 14px;"><strong><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体;">本课程不同于你之前看过或听过的任何历史课</span></strong><strong><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体;"></span></strong></span></p><p><span style="font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体;">《秦汉与罗马》这个专辑与市场上的中国通史类音频课程最大的不同是</span><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;">: </span><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体;">将中国历史放入世界史的维度中看待。从全球史观的角度，通过同时期秦汉与罗马两大文明的对照，更清楚的看到中华文明的发展轨迹、与世界其它文明的碰撞和异同。</span><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;">&nbsp;</span></span></p><p><span style="font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;"><br/></span></p><p><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appkHUDlT435887/image/ueditor/47935400_1539331816.jpg" title=".jpg" alt="秦汉与罗马课程大纲.jpg"/></p><p><br/></p><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="text-align: center; margin: 10px 0% 20px; position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="display: inline-block; width: 47%; vertical-align: top; box-shadow: rgb(140, 140, 140) 0px 0px 3px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="display: inline-block; width: 100%; vertical-align: top; padding: 15px 10px 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;">你将获得</strong></p></section></section></section></section></section></section><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px 0% -10px; position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="max-width: 100%; vertical-align: middle; display: inline-block; box-shadow: rgb(0, 0, 0) 0px 0px 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appkHUDlT435887/image/ueditor/16838100_1538623070.png" style="vertical-align: middle; box-sizing: border-box;"/></section></section></section></section></section></section></section><p class="MsoListParagraph" style="margin-left: 24px"><span style="font-size: 14px;"></span></p><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 2; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">1.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong>中西文明溯源。</strong>精讲影响世界的两大文明，从源头梳理世界文明的发展，从各个角度相互对照，审视异同。使我们有机会观赏到两种不同历史背景下诞生和发展、且迥然各异的文化，感受漫漫历史长河中两大文明的璀璨和交融；</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">2.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong>一种看待历史的新角度。</strong>从我们的眼光看世界，从世界的眼光看自己，扩展眼界，拉开你和别人的认知差距；</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">3.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong>引发思考。</strong>破除非黑即白的观念，提升看待历史的格局，提高思辨能力，不人云亦云，启发独立思考；</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">4.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong>帮助你更清晰理解东西方思维模式及文明发展轨迹。</strong></p></section></section></section></section><p class="MsoListParagraph" style="margin-left: 24px"><br/></p><p><span style="font-size: 14px;">&nbsp;</span></p><p><span style="font-size: 14px;"><br/></span></p><p><span style="font-size: 14px;"><strong><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体;"></span></strong></span></p><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="text-align: center; margin: 10px 0% 20px; position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="display: inline-block; width: 47%; vertical-align: top; box-shadow: rgb(140, 140, 140) 0px 0px 3px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="display: inline-block; width: 100%; vertical-align: top; padding: 15px 10px 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;">适合谁听？</strong></p></section></section></section></section></section></section><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px 0% -10px; position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="max-width: 100%; vertical-align: middle; display: inline-block; box-shadow: rgb(0, 0, 0) 0px 0px 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appkHUDlT435887/image/ueditor/46571100_1538623092.png" style="vertical-align: middle; box-sizing: border-box;"/></section></section></section></section></section></section></section><p><span style="font-size: 14px;"><strong><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体;"></span></strong></span><br/></p><p class="MsoListParagraph" style="margin-left: 24px"><span style="font-size: 14px;"></span></p><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 2; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">1.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;常去博物馆，对秦汉及罗马文明历史、艺术感兴趣的朋友；</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">2.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;游走欧洲，想进一步了解欧洲文明发展的朋友；</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">3.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;关注历史，热爱人文、艺术的朋友；</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">4.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;不限于关注历史，更关心世界发展未来的朋友。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p></section></section></section></section><p class="MsoListParagraph" style="margin-left: 24px"><br/></p><section style="white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 10px 0px; text-align: center; position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="text-align: center; margin: 10px 0% 20px; position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="display: inline-block; width: 47%; vertical-align: top; box-shadow: rgb(140, 140, 140) 0px 0px 3px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="display: inline-block; width: 100%; vertical-align: top; padding: 15px 10px 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">主讲人</p></section></section></section></section></section></section><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px 0% -10px; position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="max-width: 100%; vertical-align: middle; display: inline-block; box-shadow: rgb(0, 0, 0) 0px 0px 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appkHUDlT435887/image/ueditor/70422700_1538623169.png" style="vertical-align: middle; box-sizing: border-box;"/></section></section></section></section></section></section></section><p><br/></p><p style="white-space: normal;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: center;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box;"></strong></span></strong></span></p><p style="white-space: normal;"><br/></p><p><br/></p><section style="font-size: medium; white-space: normal; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; width: 7em; height: 7em; display: inline-block; vertical-align: bottom; border-radius: 100%; border-width: 5px; border-style: solid; box-shadow: rgb(204, 204, 204) 0.707107px 0.707107px 2px; border-color: white; background-position: center center; background-repeat: no-repeat; background-size: cover; background-image: url(&#39;http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appkHUDlT435887/image/ueditor/15326300_1538623343.cn/mmbiz_jpg/icetjwgztmpez1lbsybfn6gkizfib5jnrmdly6zmae0fvzoa5ianeiyfgphmj5c6rv4pyctjkiat9hu2sjaxqad6qq/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&#39;);"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 103.108px; height: 103.108px; overflow: hidden; box-sizing: border-box;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appkHUDlT435887/image/ueditor/16014800_1538623343.cn/mmbiz_jpg/icetjwgztmpez1lbsybfn6gkizfib5jnrmdly6zmae0fvzoa5ianeiyfgphmj5c6rv4pyctjkiat9hu2sjaxqad6qq/640" width="100%" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; height: 122.448px; width: 103.108px; opacity: 0; box-sizing: border-box;"/></section></section><section style="margin: -3em 0px 0px; padding: 0px 10px 10px; border-color: rgb(151, 124, 66); border-style: dotted; border-width: 2px; border-radius: 0.3em; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 3.5em 0px 15px; text-align: left; line-height: 1.8; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box; line-height: normal;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box;">廖钒</span></strong></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box; line-height: normal;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box;">资深文化艺术讲师</span></strong></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box; line-height: normal;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box;">博物馆有得聊联合创始人</span></strong></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box; line-height: normal;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;"><br/></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box; line-height: normal;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;">做一件事情坚持超过15年的就该是真爱吧。从大学开始到现在，工作换了好几个，定期去博物馆一直没变过。</span><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box; line-height: normal;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box; line-height: normal;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;">她举办了近300场讲座。已为超过8万人讲解过国家博物馆15年来举办的50余个涵盖中外文明的展览。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box; line-height: normal;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box; line-height: normal;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box;">作为领队，她的准则是：讲之前，必须自己去过见过研究过。她自费考察了亚、欧、非20余个国家130多座城市的文化遗产、博物馆和古迹，直到现在，当她看到文艺复兴的雕塑作品，仍然心潮澎湃心动不已。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box; line-height: normal;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box;">“善于发现和抓住艺术背后的历史及人文线索，在不同文明多维度全方位的视角下观察文物，并用深入浅出的语言进行解读，给人以精神层面的共鸣和享受。”这是她的粉丝给她总结的一大特点，也是她的魅力“之一”。</span></p><p style="line-height: normal;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></span></p></section></section></section></section></section></section></section><p><br/></p><p style="white-space: normal;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box; text-align: center;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(151, 124, 66); font-size: 14px;"></span></strong></p><p><br/></p></section></section></section><p><br/></p><section style="font-size: medium; white-space: normal; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; width: 7em; height: 7em; display: inline-block; vertical-align: bottom; border-radius: 100%; border-width: 5px; border-style: solid; box-shadow: rgb(204, 204, 204) 0.707107px 0.707107px 2px; border-color: white; background-position: center center; background-repeat: no-repeat; background-size: cover; background-image: url(&#39;http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appkHUDlT435887/image/ueditor/70884000_1538622842.cn/mmbiz_jpg/icetjwgztmpga7447pixc967w8a9raqjvth4vs7mraovyanz7jwgkglzzybjaqud4xr3h4ia8yuovwffu9tkduibw/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&#39;);"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 103.108px; height: 103.108px; overflow: hidden; box-sizing: border-box;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appkHUDlT435887/image/ueditor/81542900_1538622842.cn/mmbiz_jpg/icetjwgztmpga7447pixc967w8a9raqjvth4vs7mraovyanz7jwgkglzzybjaqud4xr3h4ia8yuovwffu9tkduibw/640" width="100%" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; height: 116.788px; width: 103.108px; opacity: 0; box-sizing: border-box;"/></section></section><section style="margin: -3em 0px 0px; padding: 0px 10px 10px; border-color: rgb(151, 124, 66); border-style: dotted; border-width: 2px; border-radius: 0.3em; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 3.5em 0px 15px; text-align: left; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;">冯海啸</span></strong></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;">资深文化艺术讲师</span></strong><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;"><br/></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box; text-align: center;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;"><strong style="font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: medium; text-align: center; white-space: normal; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box;">博物馆有得聊联合创始人</span></strong></span></strong></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;">2004年至今，曾长期担任拍卖公司书画部、古籍善本部业务经理，鉴定并征集齐白石《群虾图》、程十发《长吉诗意兰香神女图》、吴湖帆旧藏清汪由敦、钱维城书画合璧册页、秦权清拓本、唐海兽葡萄纹铜镜、明宣德青花缠枝莲纹折沿盆、明嘉靖五十四年项氏万卷堂刊本《前四史论赞》、明万历刊本《乡贤区西屏集》、明万历三年刻本《史记钞》、民国徐乃昌影刻明寒山赵均小宛堂本《玉台新咏》等重要文物。撰写并发表了《宋刻天禄琳琅藏本〈后村居士集〉》、《万古词章楮墨传——谈民国藏书家徐乃昌覆刻的明寒山赵氏小宛堂本〈玉台新咏〉》等文章。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;">2003年起至今，讲解各类展览20余个，为观众服务千余小时，并撰写多个展览的讲解词。</span></p><p><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;"><br/></span></p></section></section></section></section></section></section></section><section style="font-size: medium; white-space: normal; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"></section></section><p><br/></p><p style="white-space: normal;"><br/></p><p><br/></p>

第一讲：雕塑里的精神世界，击鼓说唱俑、正在沐浴的女神雕像及健陀罗风格佛像

https://fenxiao.xiaoe-tech.com/#/try_page/1/appiu7n5lWz2984/a_5c9219dec9d8a_HtOWHoqW

<p><span style="font-size: 14px;"><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;">如果历史上没有秦汉与罗马，世界将会怎样？</span></strong><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;"></span></strong></span></p><p><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;">两千多年前，在欧亚大陆的东西两端出现了两个强大的国家：秦汉和罗马。它们代表着当时古代世界文明的最高辉煌成就。</span></p><p><span style="font-size: 14px;">&nbsp;</span></p><p><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;">英国著名历史学家汤因比在其《历史研究》一书中进行文明比较研究时，提出世界文明发展的两种主要模式，即希腊模式与中国模式。在他看来，古罗马文明是希腊模式高度发展的必然结果，所谓希腊文明亦可称为希腊—罗马文明，而中国的秦汉王朝则是中国模式的开始。</span></p><p><span style="font-size: 14px;">&nbsp;<img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appkHUDlT435887/image/ueditor/28035300_1538622915.jpg" title=".jpg" alt="幻灯片1.JPG"/></span></p><p><br/></p><p><span style="font-size: 14px;"><strong><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体;">这是一门欢迎碰撞，启发你思考的历史课</span></strong><strong><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体;"></span></strong></span></p><p><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;">《秦汉与罗马》专辑结合博物馆文物研究和遗址考古等热点，梳理对照两大文明政治、经济、文化及衣食住行生活的方方面面，不仅关注创造历史的大人物，更关心历史长河中的小人物等各阶层的生活。兼顾历史知识的架构和普及、艺术的审美及博物馆游学旅行的参考指南等功能。</span></p><p><span style="font-size: 14px;">&nbsp;<img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appkHUDlT435887/image/ueditor/21884400_1538622744.jpg" title=".jpg" alt="1 (2).JPG" style="font-size: 14px; white-space: normal;"/></span></p><p><span style="font-size: 14px;"><br/></span></p><p><span style="font-size: 14px;"><strong><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体;">本课程不同于你之前看过或听过的任何历史课</span></strong><strong><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体;"></span></strong></span></p><p><span style="font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体;">《秦汉与罗马》这个专辑与市场上的中国通史类音频课程最大的不同是</span><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;">: </span><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体;">将中国历史放入世界史的维度中看待。从全球史观的角度，通过同时期秦汉与罗马两大文明的对照，更清楚的看到中华文明的发展轨迹、与世界其它文明的碰撞和异同。</span><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;">&nbsp;</span></span></p><p><span style="font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;"><br/></span></p><p><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appkHUDlT435887/image/ueditor/47935400_1539331816.jpg" title=".jpg" alt="秦汉与罗马课程大纲.jpg"/></p><p><br/></p><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="text-align: center; margin: 10px 0% 20px; position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="display: inline-block; width: 47%; vertical-align: top; box-shadow: rgb(140, 140, 140) 0px 0px 3px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="display: inline-block; width: 100%; vertical-align: top; padding: 15px 10px 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;">你将获得</strong></p></section></section></section></section></section></section><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px 0% -10px; position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="max-width: 100%; vertical-align: middle; display: inline-block; box-shadow: rgb(0, 0, 0) 0px 0px 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appkHUDlT435887/image/ueditor/16838100_1538623070.png" style="vertical-align: middle; box-sizing: border-box;"/></section></section></section></section></section></section></section><p class="MsoListParagraph" style="margin-left: 24px"><span style="font-size: 14px;"></span></p><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 2; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">1.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong>中西文明溯源。</strong>精讲影响世界的两大文明，从源头梳理世界文明的发展，从各个角度相互对照，审视异同。使我们有机会观赏到两种不同历史背景下诞生和发展、且迥然各异的文化，感受漫漫历史长河中两大文明的璀璨和交融；</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">2.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong>一种看待历史的新角度。</strong>从我们的眼光看世界，从世界的眼光看自己，扩展眼界，拉开你和别人的认知差距；</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">3.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong>引发思考。</strong>破除非黑即白的观念，提升看待历史的格局，提高思辨能力，不人云亦云，启发独立思考；</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">4.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong>帮助你更清晰理解东西方思维模式及文明发展轨迹。</strong></p></section></section></section></section><p class="MsoListParagraph" style="margin-left: 24px"><br/></p><p><span style="font-size: 14px;">&nbsp;</span></p><p><span style="font-size: 14px;"><br/></span></p><p><span style="font-size: 14px;"><strong><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体;"></span></strong></span></p><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="text-align: center; margin: 10px 0% 20px; position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="display: inline-block; width: 47%; vertical-align: top; box-shadow: rgb(140, 140, 140) 0px 0px 3px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="display: inline-block; width: 100%; vertical-align: top; padding: 15px 10px 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;">适合谁听？</strong></p></section></section></section></section></section></section><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px 0% -10px; position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="max-width: 100%; vertical-align: middle; display: inline-block; box-shadow: rgb(0, 0, 0) 0px 0px 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appkHUDlT435887/image/ueditor/46571100_1538623092.png" style="vertical-align: middle; box-sizing: border-box;"/></section></section></section></section></section></section></section><p><span style="font-size: 14px;"><strong><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体;"></span></strong></span><br/></p><p class="MsoListParagraph" style="margin-left: 24px"><span style="font-size: 14px;"></span></p><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 2; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">1.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;常去博物馆，对秦汉及罗马文明历史、艺术感兴趣的朋友；</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">2.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;游走欧洲，想进一步了解欧洲文明发展的朋友；</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">3.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;关注历史，热爱人文、艺术的朋友；</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">4.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;不限于关注历史，更关心世界发展未来的朋友。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p></section></section></section></section><p class="MsoListParagraph" style="margin-left: 24px"><br/></p><section style="white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 10px 0px; text-align: center; position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="text-align: center; margin: 10px 0% 20px; position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="display: inline-block; width: 47%; vertical-align: top; box-shadow: rgb(140, 140, 140) 0px 0px 3px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="display: inline-block; width: 100%; vertical-align: top; padding: 15px 10px 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">主讲人</p></section></section></section></section></section></section><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px 0% -10px; position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="max-width: 100%; vertical-align: middle; display: inline-block; box-shadow: rgb(0, 0, 0) 0px 0px 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appkHUDlT435887/image/ueditor/70422700_1538623169.png" style="vertical-align: middle; box-sizing: border-box;"/></section></section></section></section></section></section></section><p><br/></p><p style="white-space: normal;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: center;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box;"></strong></span></strong></span></p><p style="white-space: normal;"><br/></p><p><br/></p><section style="font-size: medium; white-space: normal; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; width: 7em; height: 7em; display: inline-block; vertical-align: bottom; border-radius: 100%; border-width: 5px; border-style: solid; box-shadow: rgb(204, 204, 204) 0.707107px 0.707107px 2px; border-color: white; background-position: center center; background-repeat: no-repeat; background-size: cover; background-image: url(&#39;http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appkHUDlT435887/image/ueditor/15326300_1538623343.cn/mmbiz_jpg/icetjwgztmpez1lbsybfn6gkizfib5jnrmdly6zmae0fvzoa5ianeiyfgphmj5c6rv4pyctjkiat9hu2sjaxqad6qq/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&#39;);"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 103.108px; height: 103.108px; overflow: hidden; box-sizing: border-box;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appkHUDlT435887/image/ueditor/16014800_1538623343.cn/mmbiz_jpg/icetjwgztmpez1lbsybfn6gkizfib5jnrmdly6zmae0fvzoa5ianeiyfgphmj5c6rv4pyctjkiat9hu2sjaxqad6qq/640" width="100%" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; height: 122.448px; width: 103.108px; opacity: 0; box-sizing: border-box;"/></section></section><section style="margin: -3em 0px 0px; padding: 0px 10px 10px; border-color: rgb(151, 124, 66); border-style: dotted; border-width: 2px; border-radius: 0.3em; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 3.5em 0px 15px; text-align: left; line-height: 1.8; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box; line-height: normal;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box;">廖钒</span></strong></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box; line-height: normal;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box;">资深文化艺术讲师</span></strong></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box; line-height: normal;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box;">博物馆有得聊联合创始人</span></strong></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box; line-height: normal;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;"><br/></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box; line-height: normal;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;">做一件事情坚持超过15年的就该是真爱吧。从大学开始到现在，工作换了好几个，定期去博物馆一直没变过。</span><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box; line-height: normal;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box; line-height: normal;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;">她举办了近300场讲座。已为超过8万人讲解过国家博物馆15年来举办的50余个涵盖中外文明的展览。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box; line-height: normal;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box; line-height: normal;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box;">作为领队，她的准则是：讲之前，必须自己去过见过研究过。她自费考察了亚、欧、非20余个国家130多座城市的文化遗产、博物馆和古迹，直到现在，当她看到文艺复兴的雕塑作品，仍然心潮澎湃心动不已。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box; line-height: normal;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box;">“善于发现和抓住艺术背后的历史及人文线索，在不同文明多维度全方位的视角下观察文物，并用深入浅出的语言进行解读，给人以精神层面的共鸣和享受。”这是她的粉丝给她总结的一大特点，也是她的魅力“之一”。</span></p><p style="line-height: normal;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></span></p></section></section></section></section></section></section></section><p><br/></p><p style="white-space: normal;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box; text-align: center;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(151, 124, 66); font-size: 14px;"></span></strong></p><p><br/></p></section></section></section><p><br/></p><section style="font-size: medium; white-space: normal; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; width: 7em; height: 7em; display: inline-block; vertical-align: bottom; border-radius: 100%; border-width: 5px; border-style: solid; box-shadow: rgb(204, 204, 204) 0.707107px 0.707107px 2px; border-color: white; background-position: center center; background-repeat: no-repeat; background-size: cover; background-image: url(&#39;http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appkHUDlT435887/image/ueditor/70884000_1538622842.cn/mmbiz_jpg/icetjwgztmpga7447pixc967w8a9raqjvth4vs7mraovyanz7jwgkglzzybjaqud4xr3h4ia8yuovwffu9tkduibw/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&#39;);"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 103.108px; height: 103.108px; overflow: hidden; box-sizing: border-box;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appkHUDlT435887/image/ueditor/81542900_1538622842.cn/mmbiz_jpg/icetjwgztmpga7447pixc967w8a9raqjvth4vs7mraovyanz7jwgkglzzybjaqud4xr3h4ia8yuovwffu9tkduibw/640" width="100%" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; height: 116.788px; width: 103.108px; opacity: 0; box-sizing: border-box;"/></section></section><section style="margin: -3em 0px 0px; padding: 0px 10px 10px; border-color: rgb(151, 124, 66); border-style: dotted; border-width: 2px; border-radius: 0.3em; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 3.5em 0px 15px; text-align: left; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;">冯海啸</span></strong></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;">资深文化艺术讲师</span></strong><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;"><br/></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box; text-align: center;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;"><strong style="font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: medium; text-align: center; white-space: normal; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box;">博物馆有得聊联合创始人</span></strong></span></strong></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;">2004年至今，曾长期担任拍卖公司书画部、古籍善本部业务经理，鉴定并征集齐白石《群虾图》、程十发《长吉诗意兰香神女图》、吴湖帆旧藏清汪由敦、钱维城书画合璧册页、秦权清拓本、唐海兽葡萄纹铜镜、明宣德青花缠枝莲纹折沿盆、明嘉靖五十四年项氏万卷堂刊本《前四史论赞》、明万历刊本《乡贤区西屏集》、明万历三年刻本《史记钞》、民国徐乃昌影刻明寒山赵均小宛堂本《玉台新咏》等重要文物。撰写并发表了《宋刻天禄琳琅藏本〈后村居士集〉》、《万古词章楮墨传——谈民国藏书家徐乃昌覆刻的明寒山赵氏小宛堂本〈玉台新咏〉》等文章。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;">2003年起至今，讲解各类展览20余个，为观众服务千余小时，并撰写多个展览的讲解词。</span></p><p><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;"><br/></span></p></section></section></section></section></section></section></section><section style="font-size: medium; white-space: normal; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"></section></section><p><br/></p><p style="white-space: normal;"><br/></p><p><br/></p>

第二讲：写意写实大不同，武梁祠画像砖和奥秘别墅壁画

https://fenxiao.xiaoe-tech.com/#/try_page/1/appITMzqTKJ8910/a_5c9219dec9d44_2e3LA68s

<p><span style="font-size: 14px;"><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;">如果历史上没有秦汉与罗马，世界将会怎样？</span></strong><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;"></span></strong></span></p><p><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;">两千多年前，在欧亚大陆的东西两端出现了两个强大的国家：秦汉和罗马。它们代表着当时古代世界文明的最高辉煌成就。</span></p><p><span style="font-size: 14px;">&nbsp;</span></p><p><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;">英国著名历史学家汤因比在其《历史研究》一书中进行文明比较研究时，提出世界文明发展的两种主要模式，即希腊模式与中国模式。在他看来，古罗马文明是希腊模式高度发展的必然结果，所谓希腊文明亦可称为希腊—罗马文明，而中国的秦汉王朝则是中国模式的开始。</span></p><p><span style="font-size: 14px;">&nbsp;<img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appkHUDlT435887/image/ueditor/28035300_1538622915.jpg" title=".jpg" alt="幻灯片1.JPG"/></span></p><p><br/></p><p><span style="font-size: 14px;"><strong><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体;">这是一门欢迎碰撞，启发你思考的历史课</span></strong><strong><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体;"></span></strong></span></p><p><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;">《秦汉与罗马》专辑结合博物馆文物研究和遗址考古等热点，梳理对照两大文明政治、经济、文化及衣食住行生活的方方面面，不仅关注创造历史的大人物，更关心历史长河中的小人物等各阶层的生活。兼顾历史知识的架构和普及、艺术的审美及博物馆游学旅行的参考指南等功能。</span></p><p><span style="font-size: 14px;">&nbsp;<img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appkHUDlT435887/image/ueditor/21884400_1538622744.jpg" title=".jpg" alt="1 (2).JPG" style="font-size: 14px; white-space: normal;"/></span></p><p><span style="font-size: 14px;"><br/></span></p><p><span style="font-size: 14px;"><strong><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体;">本课程不同于你之前看过或听过的任何历史课</span></strong><strong><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体;"></span></strong></span></p><p><span style="font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体;">《秦汉与罗马》这个专辑与市场上的中国通史类音频课程最大的不同是</span><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;">: </span><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体;">将中国历史放入世界史的维度中看待。从全球史观的角度，通过同时期秦汉与罗马两大文明的对照，更清楚的看到中华文明的发展轨迹、与世界其它文明的碰撞和异同。</span><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;">&nbsp;</span></span></p><p><span style="font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;"><br/></span></p><p><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appkHUDlT435887/image/ueditor/47935400_1539331816.jpg" title=".jpg" alt="秦汉与罗马课程大纲.jpg"/></p><p><br/></p><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="text-align: center; margin: 10px 0% 20px; position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="display: inline-block; width: 47%; vertical-align: top; box-shadow: rgb(140, 140, 140) 0px 0px 3px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="display: inline-block; width: 100%; vertical-align: top; padding: 15px 10px 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;">你将获得</strong></p></section></section></section></section></section></section><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px 0% -10px; position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="max-width: 100%; vertical-align: middle; display: inline-block; box-shadow: rgb(0, 0, 0) 0px 0px 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appkHUDlT435887/image/ueditor/16838100_1538623070.png" style="vertical-align: middle; box-sizing: border-box;"/></section></section></section></section></section></section></section><p class="MsoListParagraph" style="margin-left: 24px"><span style="font-size: 14px;"></span></p><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 2; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">1.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong>中西文明溯源。</strong>精讲影响世界的两大文明，从源头梳理世界文明的发展，从各个角度相互对照，审视异同。使我们有机会观赏到两种不同历史背景下诞生和发展、且迥然各异的文化，感受漫漫历史长河中两大文明的璀璨和交融；</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">2.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong>一种看待历史的新角度。</strong>从我们的眼光看世界，从世界的眼光看自己，扩展眼界，拉开你和别人的认知差距；</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">3.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong>引发思考。</strong>破除非黑即白的观念，提升看待历史的格局，提高思辨能力，不人云亦云，启发独立思考；</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">4.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong>帮助你更清晰理解东西方思维模式及文明发展轨迹。</strong></p></section></section></section></section><p class="MsoListParagraph" style="margin-left: 24px"><br/></p><p><span style="font-size: 14px;">&nbsp;</span></p><p><span style="font-size: 14px;"><br/></span></p><p><span style="font-size: 14px;"><strong><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体;"></span></strong></span></p><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="text-align: center; margin: 10px 0% 20px; position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="display: inline-block; width: 47%; vertical-align: top; box-shadow: rgb(140, 140, 140) 0px 0px 3px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="display: inline-block; width: 100%; vertical-align: top; padding: 15px 10px 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;">适合谁听？</strong></p></section></section></section></section></section></section><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px 0% -10px; position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="max-width: 100%; vertical-align: middle; display: inline-block; box-shadow: rgb(0, 0, 0) 0px 0px 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appkHUDlT435887/image/ueditor/46571100_1538623092.png" style="vertical-align: middle; box-sizing: border-box;"/></section></section></section></section></section></section></section><p><span style="font-size: 14px;"><strong><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体;"></span></strong></span><br/></p><p class="MsoListParagraph" style="margin-left: 24px"><span style="font-size: 14px;"></span></p><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 2; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">1.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;常去博物馆，对秦汉及罗马文明历史、艺术感兴趣的朋友；</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">2.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;游走欧洲，想进一步了解欧洲文明发展的朋友；</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">3.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;关注历史，热爱人文、艺术的朋友；</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">4.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;不限于关注历史，更关心世界发展未来的朋友。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p></section></section></section></section><p class="MsoListParagraph" style="margin-left: 24px"><br/></p><section style="white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 10px 0px; text-align: center; position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="text-align: center; margin: 10px 0% 20px; position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="display: inline-block; width: 47%; vertical-align: top; box-shadow: rgb(140, 140, 140) 0px 0px 3px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="display: inline-block; width: 100%; vertical-align: top; padding: 15px 10px 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">主讲人</p></section></section></section></section></section></section><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px 0% -10px; position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="max-width: 100%; vertical-align: middle; display: inline-block; box-shadow: rgb(0, 0, 0) 0px 0px 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appkHUDlT435887/image/ueditor/70422700_1538623169.png" style="vertical-align: middle; box-sizing: border-box;"/></section></section></section></section></section></section></section><p><br/></p><p style="white-space: normal;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: center;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box;"></strong></span></strong></span></p><p style="white-space: normal;"><br/></p><p><br/></p><section style="font-size: medium; white-space: normal; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; width: 7em; height: 7em; display: inline-block; vertical-align: bottom; border-radius: 100%; border-width: 5px; border-style: solid; box-shadow: rgb(204, 204, 204) 0.707107px 0.707107px 2px; border-color: white; background-position: center center; background-repeat: no-repeat; background-size: cover; background-image: url(&#39;http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appkHUDlT435887/image/ueditor/15326300_1538623343.cn/mmbiz_jpg/icetjwgztmpez1lbsybfn6gkizfib5jnrmdly6zmae0fvzoa5ianeiyfgphmj5c6rv4pyctjkiat9hu2sjaxqad6qq/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&#39;);"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 103.108px; height: 103.108px; overflow: hidden; box-sizing: border-box;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appkHUDlT435887/image/ueditor/16014800_1538623343.cn/mmbiz_jpg/icetjwgztmpez1lbsybfn6gkizfib5jnrmdly6zmae0fvzoa5ianeiyfgphmj5c6rv4pyctjkiat9hu2sjaxqad6qq/640" width="100%" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; height: 122.448px; width: 103.108px; opacity: 0; box-sizing: border-box;"/></section></section><section style="margin: -3em 0px 0px; padding: 0px 10px 10px; border-color: rgb(151, 124, 66); border-style: dotted; border-width: 2px; border-radius: 0.3em; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 3.5em 0px 15px; text-align: left; line-height: 1.8; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box; line-height: normal;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box;">廖钒</span></strong></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box; line-height: normal;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box;">资深文化艺术讲师</span></strong></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box; line-height: normal;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box;">博物馆有得聊联合创始人</span></strong></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box; line-height: normal;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;"><br/></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box; line-height: normal;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;">做一件事情坚持超过15年的就该是真爱吧。从大学开始到现在，工作换了好几个，定期去博物馆一直没变过。</span><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box; line-height: normal;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box; line-height: normal;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;">她举办了近300场讲座。已为超过8万人讲解过国家博物馆15年来举办的50余个涵盖中外文明的展览。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box; line-height: normal;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box; line-height: normal;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box;">作为领队，她的准则是：讲之前，必须自己去过见过研究过。她自费考察了亚、欧、非20余个国家130多座城市的文化遗产、博物馆和古迹，直到现在，当她看到文艺复兴的雕塑作品，仍然心潮澎湃心动不已。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box; line-height: normal;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box;">“善于发现和抓住艺术背后的历史及人文线索，在不同文明多维度全方位的视角下观察文物，并用深入浅出的语言进行解读，给人以精神层面的共鸣和享受。”这是她的粉丝给她总结的一大特点，也是她的魅力“之一”。</span></p><p style="line-height: normal;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></span></p></section></section></section></section></section></section></section><p><br/></p><p style="white-space: normal;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box; text-align: center;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(151, 124, 66); font-size: 14px;"></span></strong></p><p><br/></p></section></section></section><p><br/></p><section style="font-size: medium; white-space: normal; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; width: 7em; height: 7em; display: inline-block; vertical-align: bottom; border-radius: 100%; border-width: 5px; border-style: solid; box-shadow: rgb(204, 204, 204) 0.707107px 0.707107px 2px; border-color: white; background-position: center center; background-repeat: no-repeat; background-size: cover; background-image: url(&#39;http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appkHUDlT435887/image/ueditor/70884000_1538622842.cn/mmbiz_jpg/icetjwgztmpga7447pixc967w8a9raqjvth4vs7mraovyanz7jwgkglzzybjaqud4xr3h4ia8yuovwffu9tkduibw/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&#39;);"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 103.108px; height: 103.108px; overflow: hidden; box-sizing: border-box;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appkHUDlT435887/image/ueditor/81542900_1538622842.cn/mmbiz_jpg/icetjwgztmpga7447pixc967w8a9raqjvth4vs7mraovyanz7jwgkglzzybjaqud4xr3h4ia8yuovwffu9tkduibw/640" width="100%" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; height: 116.788px; width: 103.108px; opacity: 0; box-sizing: border-box;"/></section></section><section style="margin: -3em 0px 0px; padding: 0px 10px 10px; border-color: rgb(151, 124, 66); border-style: dotted; border-width: 2px; border-radius: 0.3em; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 3.5em 0px 15px; text-align: left; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;">冯海啸</span></strong></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;">资深文化艺术讲师</span></strong><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;"><br/></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box; text-align: center;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;"><strong style="font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: medium; text-align: center; white-space: normal; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box;">博物馆有得聊联合创始人</span></strong></span></strong></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;">2004年至今，曾长期担任拍卖公司书画部、古籍善本部业务经理，鉴定并征集齐白石《群虾图》、程十发《长吉诗意兰香神女图》、吴湖帆旧藏清汪由敦、钱维城书画合璧册页、秦权清拓本、唐海兽葡萄纹铜镜、明宣德青花缠枝莲纹折沿盆、明嘉靖五十四年项氏万卷堂刊本《前四史论赞》、明万历刊本《乡贤区西屏集》、明万历三年刻本《史记钞》、民国徐乃昌影刻明寒山赵均小宛堂本《玉台新咏》等重要文物。撰写并发表了《宋刻天禄琳琅藏本〈后村居士集〉》、《万古词章楮墨传——谈民国藏书家徐乃昌覆刻的明寒山赵氏小宛堂本〈玉台新咏〉》等文章。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;">2003年起至今，讲解各类展览20余个，为观众服务千余小时，并撰写多个展览的讲解词。</span></p><p><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;"><br/></span></p></section></section></section></section></section></section></section><section style="font-size: medium; white-space: normal; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"></section></section><p><br/></p><p style="white-space: normal;"><br/></p><p><br/></p>

第三讲：同唱一首“长城谣”，秦汉长城与哈德良长城

https://fenxiao.xiaoe-tech.com/#/try_page/1/appLGcClvv27956/a_5c9219dec9cf4_zQIGM8H1

<p><span style="font-size: 14px;"><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;">如果历史上没有秦汉与罗马，世界将会怎样？</span></strong><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;"></span></strong></span></p><p><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;">两千多年前，在欧亚大陆的东西两端出现了两个强大的国家：秦汉和罗马。它们代表着当时古代世界文明的最高辉煌成就。</span></p><p><span style="font-size: 14px;">&nbsp;</span></p><p><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;">英国著名历史学家汤因比在其《历史研究》一书中进行文明比较研究时，提出世界文明发展的两种主要模式，即希腊模式与中国模式。在他看来，古罗马文明是希腊模式高度发展的必然结果，所谓希腊文明亦可称为希腊—罗马文明，而中国的秦汉王朝则是中国模式的开始。</span></p><p><span style="font-size: 14px;">&nbsp;<img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appkHUDlT435887/image/ueditor/28035300_1538622915.jpg" title=".jpg" alt="幻灯片1.JPG"/></span></p><p><br/></p><p><span style="font-size: 14px;"><strong><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体;">这是一门欢迎碰撞，启发你思考的历史课</span></strong><strong><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体;"></span></strong></span></p><p><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;">《秦汉与罗马》专辑结合博物馆文物研究和遗址考古等热点，梳理对照两大文明政治、经济、文化及衣食住行生活的方方面面，不仅关注创造历史的大人物，更关心历史长河中的小人物等各阶层的生活。兼顾历史知识的架构和普及、艺术的审美及博物馆游学旅行的参考指南等功能。</span></p><p><span style="font-size: 14px;">&nbsp;<img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appkHUDlT435887/image/ueditor/21884400_1538622744.jpg" title=".jpg" alt="1 (2).JPG" style="font-size: 14px; white-space: normal;"/></span></p><p><span style="font-size: 14px;"><br/></span></p><p><span style="font-size: 14px;"><strong><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体;">本课程不同于你之前看过或听过的任何历史课</span></strong><strong><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体;"></span></strong></span></p><p><span style="font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体;">《秦汉与罗马》这个专辑与市场上的中国通史类音频课程最大的不同是</span><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;">: </span><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体;">将中国历史放入世界史的维度中看待。从全球史观的角度，通过同时期秦汉与罗马两大文明的对照，更清楚的看到中华文明的发展轨迹、与世界其它文明的碰撞和异同。</span><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;">&nbsp;</span></span></p><p><span style="font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;"><br/></span></p><p><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appkHUDlT435887/image/ueditor/47935400_1539331816.jpg" title=".jpg" alt="秦汉与罗马课程大纲.jpg"/></p><p><br/></p><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="text-align: center; margin: 10px 0% 20px; position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="display: inline-block; width: 47%; vertical-align: top; box-shadow: rgb(140, 140, 140) 0px 0px 3px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="display: inline-block; width: 100%; vertical-align: top; padding: 15px 10px 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;">你将获得</strong></p></section></section></section></section></section></section><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px 0% -10px; position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="max-width: 100%; vertical-align: middle; display: inline-block; box-shadow: rgb(0, 0, 0) 0px 0px 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appkHUDlT435887/image/ueditor/16838100_1538623070.png" style="vertical-align: middle; box-sizing: border-box;"/></section></section></section></section></section></section></section><p class="MsoListParagraph" style="margin-left: 24px"><span style="font-size: 14px;"></span></p><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 2; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">1.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong>中西文明溯源。</strong>精讲影响世界的两大文明，从源头梳理世界文明的发展，从各个角度相互对照，审视异同。使我们有机会观赏到两种不同历史背景下诞生和发展、且迥然各异的文化，感受漫漫历史长河中两大文明的璀璨和交融；</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">2.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong>一种看待历史的新角度。</strong>从我们的眼光看世界，从世界的眼光看自己，扩展眼界，拉开你和别人的认知差距；</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">3.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong>引发思考。</strong>破除非黑即白的观念，提升看待历史的格局，提高思辨能力，不人云亦云，启发独立思考；</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">4.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong>帮助你更清晰理解东西方思维模式及文明发展轨迹。</strong></p></section></section></section></section><p class="MsoListParagraph" style="margin-left: 24px"><br/></p><p><span style="font-size: 14px;">&nbsp;</span></p><p><span style="font-size: 14px;"><br/></span></p><p><span style="font-size: 14px;"><strong><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体;"></span></strong></span></p><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="text-align: center; margin: 10px 0% 20px; position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="display: inline-block; width: 47%; vertical-align: top; box-shadow: rgb(140, 140, 140) 0px 0px 3px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="display: inline-block; width: 100%; vertical-align: top; padding: 15px 10px 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;">适合谁听？</strong></p></section></section></section></section></section></section><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px 0% -10px; position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="max-width: 100%; vertical-align: middle; display: inline-block; box-shadow: rgb(0, 0, 0) 0px 0px 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appkHUDlT435887/image/ueditor/46571100_1538623092.png" style="vertical-align: middle; box-sizing: border-box;"/></section></section></section></section></section></section></section><p><span style="font-size: 14px;"><strong><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体;"></span></strong></span><br/></p><p class="MsoListParagraph" style="margin-left: 24px"><span style="font-size: 14px;"></span></p><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 2; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">1.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;常去博物馆，对秦汉及罗马文明历史、艺术感兴趣的朋友；</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">2.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;游走欧洲，想进一步了解欧洲文明发展的朋友；</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">3.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;关注历史，热爱人文、艺术的朋友；</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">4.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;不限于关注历史，更关心世界发展未来的朋友。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p></section></section></section></section><p class="MsoListParagraph" style="margin-left: 24px"><br/></p><section style="white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 10px 0px; text-align: center; position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="text-align: center; margin: 10px 0% 20px; position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="display: inline-block; width: 47%; vertical-align: top; box-shadow: rgb(140, 140, 140) 0px 0px 3px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="display: inline-block; width: 100%; vertical-align: top; padding: 15px 10px 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">主讲人</p></section></section></section></section></section></section><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px 0% -10px; position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="max-width: 100%; vertical-align: middle; display: inline-block; box-shadow: rgb(0, 0, 0) 0px 0px 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appkHUDlT435887/image/ueditor/70422700_1538623169.png" style="vertical-align: middle; box-sizing: border-box;"/></section></section></section></section></section></section></section><p><br/></p><p style="white-space: normal;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: center;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box;"></strong></span></strong></span></p><p style="white-space: normal;"><br/></p><p><br/></p><section style="font-size: medium; white-space: normal; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; width: 7em; height: 7em; display: inline-block; vertical-align: bottom; border-radius: 100%; border-width: 5px; border-style: solid; box-shadow: rgb(204, 204, 204) 0.707107px 0.707107px 2px; border-color: white; background-position: center center; background-repeat: no-repeat; background-size: cover; background-image: url(&#39;http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appkHUDlT435887/image/ueditor/15326300_1538623343.cn/mmbiz_jpg/icetjwgztmpez1lbsybfn6gkizfib5jnrmdly6zmae0fvzoa5ianeiyfgphmj5c6rv4pyctjkiat9hu2sjaxqad6qq/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&#39;);"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 103.108px; height: 103.108px; overflow: hidden; box-sizing: border-box;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appkHUDlT435887/image/ueditor/16014800_1538623343.cn/mmbiz_jpg/icetjwgztmpez1lbsybfn6gkizfib5jnrmdly6zmae0fvzoa5ianeiyfgphmj5c6rv4pyctjkiat9hu2sjaxqad6qq/640" width="100%" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; height: 122.448px; width: 103.108px; opacity: 0; box-sizing: border-box;"/></section></section><section style="margin: -3em 0px 0px; padding: 0px 10px 10px; border-color: rgb(151, 124, 66); border-style: dotted; border-width: 2px; border-radius: 0.3em; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 3.5em 0px 15px; text-align: left; line-height: 1.8; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box; line-height: normal;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box;">廖钒</span></strong></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box; line-height: normal;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box;">资深文化艺术讲师</span></strong></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box; line-height: normal;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box;">博物馆有得聊联合创始人</span></strong></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box; line-height: normal;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;"><br/></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box; line-height: normal;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;">做一件事情坚持超过15年的就该是真爱吧。从大学开始到现在，工作换了好几个，定期去博物馆一直没变过。</span><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box; line-height: normal;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box; line-height: normal;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;">她举办了近300场讲座。已为超过8万人讲解过国家博物馆15年来举办的50余个涵盖中外文明的展览。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box; line-height: normal;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box; line-height: normal;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box;">作为领队，她的准则是：讲之前，必须自己去过见过研究过。她自费考察了亚、欧、非20余个国家130多座城市的文化遗产、博物馆和古迹，直到现在，当她看到文艺复兴的雕塑作品，仍然心潮澎湃心动不已。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box; line-height: normal;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box;">“善于发现和抓住艺术背后的历史及人文线索，在不同文明多维度全方位的视角下观察文物，并用深入浅出的语言进行解读，给人以精神层面的共鸣和享受。”这是她的粉丝给她总结的一大特点，也是她的魅力“之一”。</span></p><p style="line-height: normal;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></span></p></section></section></section></section></section></section></section><p><br/></p><p style="white-space: normal;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box; text-align: center;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(151, 124, 66); font-size: 14px;"></span></strong></p><p><br/></p></section></section></section><p><br/></p><section style="font-size: medium; white-space: normal; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; width: 7em; height: 7em; display: inline-block; vertical-align: bottom; border-radius: 100%; border-width: 5px; border-style: solid; box-shadow: rgb(204, 204, 204) 0.707107px 0.707107px 2px; border-color: white; background-position: center center; background-repeat: no-repeat; background-size: cover; background-image: url(&#39;http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appkHUDlT435887/image/ueditor/70884000_1538622842.cn/mmbiz_jpg/icetjwgztmpga7447pixc967w8a9raqjvth4vs7mraovyanz7jwgkglzzybjaqud4xr3h4ia8yuovwffu9tkduibw/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&#39;);"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 103.108px; height: 103.108px; overflow: hidden; box-sizing: border-box;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appkHUDlT435887/image/ueditor/81542900_1538622842.cn/mmbiz_jpg/icetjwgztmpga7447pixc967w8a9raqjvth4vs7mraovyanz7jwgkglzzybjaqud4xr3h4ia8yuovwffu9tkduibw/640" width="100%" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; height: 116.788px; width: 103.108px; opacity: 0; box-sizing: border-box;"/></section></section><section style="margin: -3em 0px 0px; padding: 0px 10px 10px; border-color: rgb(151, 124, 66); border-style: dotted; border-width: 2px; border-radius: 0.3em; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 3.5em 0px 15px; text-align: left; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;">冯海啸</span></strong></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;">资深文化艺术讲师</span></strong><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;"><br/></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box; text-align: center;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;"><strong style="font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: medium; text-align: center; white-space: normal; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box;">博物馆有得聊联合创始人</span></strong></span></strong></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;">2004年至今，曾长期担任拍卖公司书画部、古籍善本部业务经理，鉴定并征集齐白石《群虾图》、程十发《长吉诗意兰香神女图》、吴湖帆旧藏清汪由敦、钱维城书画合璧册页、秦权清拓本、唐海兽葡萄纹铜镜、明宣德青花缠枝莲纹折沿盆、明嘉靖五十四年项氏万卷堂刊本《前四史论赞》、明万历刊本《乡贤区西屏集》、明万历三年刻本《史记钞》、民国徐乃昌影刻明寒山赵均小宛堂本《玉台新咏》等重要文物。撰写并发表了《宋刻天禄琳琅藏本〈后村居士集〉》、《万古词章楮墨传——谈民国藏书家徐乃昌覆刻的明寒山赵氏小宛堂本〈玉台新咏〉》等文章。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;">2003年起至今，讲解各类展览20余个，为观众服务千余小时，并撰写多个展览的讲解词。</span></p><p><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;"><br/></span></p></section></section></section></section></section></section></section><section style="font-size: medium; white-space: normal; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"></section></section><p><br/></p><p style="white-space: normal;"><br/></p><p><br/></p>

第四讲：衣袂飘飘，绕襟衣长袖舞女俑和古罗马托加袍

https://fenxiao.xiaoe-tech.com/#/try_page/1/appIA30jiZ03636/a_5c9219dec9ca9_0t6Stw1o

<p><span style="font-size: 14px;"><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;">如果历史上没有秦汉与罗马，世界将会怎样？</span></strong><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;"></span></strong></span></p><p><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;">两千多年前，在欧亚大陆的东西两端出现了两个强大的国家：秦汉和罗马。它们代表着当时古代世界文明的最高辉煌成就。</span></p><p><span style="font-size: 14px;">&nbsp;</span></p><p><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;">英国著名历史学家汤因比在其《历史研究》一书中进行文明比较研究时，提出世界文明发展的两种主要模式，即希腊模式与中国模式。在他看来，古罗马文明是希腊模式高度发展的必然结果，所谓希腊文明亦可称为希腊—罗马文明，而中国的秦汉王朝则是中国模式的开始。</span></p><p><span style="font-size: 14px;">&nbsp;<img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appkHUDlT435887/image/ueditor/28035300_1538622915.jpg" title=".jpg" alt="幻灯片1.JPG"/></span></p><p><br/></p><p><span style="font-size: 14px;"><strong><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体;">这是一门欢迎碰撞，启发你思考的历史课</span></strong><strong><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体;"></span></strong></span></p><p><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;">《秦汉与罗马》专辑结合博物馆文物研究和遗址考古等热点，梳理对照两大文明政治、经济、文化及衣食住行生活的方方面面，不仅关注创造历史的大人物，更关心历史长河中的小人物等各阶层的生活。兼顾历史知识的架构和普及、艺术的审美及博物馆游学旅行的参考指南等功能。</span></p><p><span style="font-size: 14px;">&nbsp;<img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appkHUDlT435887/image/ueditor/21884400_1538622744.jpg" title=".jpg" alt="1 (2).JPG" style="font-size: 14px; white-space: normal;"/></span></p><p><span style="font-size: 14px;"><br/></span></p><p><span style="font-size: 14px;"><strong><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体;">本课程不同于你之前看过或听过的任何历史课</span></strong><strong><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体;"></span></strong></span></p><p><span style="font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体;">《秦汉与罗马》这个专辑与市场上的中国通史类音频课程最大的不同是</span><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;">: </span><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体;">将中国历史放入世界史的维度中看待。从全球史观的角度，通过同时期秦汉与罗马两大文明的对照，更清楚的看到中华文明的发展轨迹、与世界其它文明的碰撞和异同。</span><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;">&nbsp;</span></span></p><p><span style="font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;"><br/></span></p><p><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appkHUDlT435887/image/ueditor/47935400_1539331816.jpg" title=".jpg" alt="秦汉与罗马课程大纲.jpg"/></p><p><br/></p><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="text-align: center; margin: 10px 0% 20px; position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="display: inline-block; width: 47%; vertical-align: top; box-shadow: rgb(140, 140, 140) 0px 0px 3px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="display: inline-block; width: 100%; vertical-align: top; padding: 15px 10px 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;">你将获得</strong></p></section></section></section></section></section></section><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px 0% -10px; position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="max-width: 100%; vertical-align: middle; display: inline-block; box-shadow: rgb(0, 0, 0) 0px 0px 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appkHUDlT435887/image/ueditor/16838100_1538623070.png" style="vertical-align: middle; box-sizing: border-box;"/></section></section></section></section></section></section></section><p class="MsoListParagraph" style="margin-left: 24px"><span style="font-size: 14px;"></span></p><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 2; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">1.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong>中西文明溯源。</strong>精讲影响世界的两大文明，从源头梳理世界文明的发展，从各个角度相互对照，审视异同。使我们有机会观赏到两种不同历史背景下诞生和发展、且迥然各异的文化，感受漫漫历史长河中两大文明的璀璨和交融；</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">2.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong>一种看待历史的新角度。</strong>从我们的眼光看世界，从世界的眼光看自己，扩展眼界，拉开你和别人的认知差距；</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">3.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong>引发思考。</strong>破除非黑即白的观念，提升看待历史的格局，提高思辨能力，不人云亦云，启发独立思考；</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">4.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong>帮助你更清晰理解东西方思维模式及文明发展轨迹。</strong></p></section></section></section></section><p class="MsoListParagraph" style="margin-left: 24px"><br/></p><p><span style="font-size: 14px;">&nbsp;</span></p><p><span style="font-size: 14px;"><br/></span></p><p><span style="font-size: 14px;"><strong><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体;"></span></strong></span></p><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="text-align: center; margin: 10px 0% 20px; position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="display: inline-block; width: 47%; vertical-align: top; box-shadow: rgb(140, 140, 140) 0px 0px 3px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="display: inline-block; width: 100%; vertical-align: top; padding: 15px 10px 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;">适合谁听？</strong></p></section></section></section></section></section></section><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px 0% -10px; position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="max-width: 100%; vertical-align: middle; display: inline-block; box-shadow: rgb(0, 0, 0) 0px 0px 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appkHUDlT435887/image/ueditor/46571100_1538623092.png" style="vertical-align: middle; box-sizing: border-box;"/></section></section></section></section></section></section></section><p><span style="font-size: 14px;"><strong><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体;"></span></strong></span><br/></p><p class="MsoListParagraph" style="margin-left: 24px"><span style="font-size: 14px;"></span></p><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 2; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">1.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;常去博物馆，对秦汉及罗马文明历史、艺术感兴趣的朋友；</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">2.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;游走欧洲，想进一步了解欧洲文明发展的朋友；</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">3.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;关注历史，热爱人文、艺术的朋友；</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">4.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;不限于关注历史，更关心世界发展未来的朋友。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p></section></section></section></section><p class="MsoListParagraph" style="margin-left: 24px"><br/></p><section style="white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 10px 0px; text-align: center; position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="text-align: center; margin: 10px 0% 20px; position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="display: inline-block; width: 47%; vertical-align: top; box-shadow: rgb(140, 140, 140) 0px 0px 3px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="display: inline-block; width: 100%; vertical-align: top; padding: 15px 10px 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">主讲人</p></section></section></section></section></section></section><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px 0% -10px; position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="max-width: 100%; vertical-align: middle; display: inline-block; box-shadow: rgb(0, 0, 0) 0px 0px 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appkHUDlT435887/image/ueditor/70422700_1538623169.png" style="vertical-align: middle; box-sizing: border-box;"/></section></section></section></section></section></section></section><p><br/></p><p style="white-space: normal;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: center;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box;"></strong></span></strong></span></p><p style="white-space: normal;"><br/></p><p><br/></p><section style="font-size: medium; white-space: normal; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; width: 7em; height: 7em; display: inline-block; vertical-align: bottom; border-radius: 100%; border-width: 5px; border-style: solid; box-shadow: rgb(204, 204, 204) 0.707107px 0.707107px 2px; border-color: white; background-position: center center; background-repeat: no-repeat; background-size: cover; background-image: url(&#39;http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appkHUDlT435887/image/ueditor/15326300_1538623343.cn/mmbiz_jpg/icetjwgztmpez1lbsybfn6gkizfib5jnrmdly6zmae0fvzoa5ianeiyfgphmj5c6rv4pyctjkiat9hu2sjaxqad6qq/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&#39;);"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 103.108px; height: 103.108px; overflow: hidden; box-sizing: border-box;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appkHUDlT435887/image/ueditor/16014800_1538623343.cn/mmbiz_jpg/icetjwgztmpez1lbsybfn6gkizfib5jnrmdly6zmae0fvzoa5ianeiyfgphmj5c6rv4pyctjkiat9hu2sjaxqad6qq/640" width="100%" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; height: 122.448px; width: 103.108px; opacity: 0; box-sizing: border-box;"/></section></section><section style="margin: -3em 0px 0px; padding: 0px 10px 10px; border-color: rgb(151, 124, 66); border-style: dotted; border-width: 2px; border-radius: 0.3em; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 3.5em 0px 15px; text-align: left; line-height: 1.8; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box; line-height: normal;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box;">廖钒</span></strong></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box; line-height: normal;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box;">资深文化艺术讲师</span></strong></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box; line-height: normal;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box;">博物馆有得聊联合创始人</span></strong></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box; line-height: normal;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;"><br/></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box; line-height: normal;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;">做一件事情坚持超过15年的就该是真爱吧。从大学开始到现在，工作换了好几个，定期去博物馆一直没变过。</span><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box; line-height: normal;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box; line-height: normal;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;">她举办了近300场讲座。已为超过8万人讲解过国家博物馆15年来举办的50余个涵盖中外文明的展览。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box; line-height: normal;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box; line-height: normal;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box;">作为领队，她的准则是：讲之前，必须自己去过见过研究过。她自费考察了亚、欧、非20余个国家130多座城市的文化遗产、博物馆和古迹，直到现在，当她看到文艺复兴的雕塑作品，仍然心潮澎湃心动不已。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box; line-height: normal;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box;">“善于发现和抓住艺术背后的历史及人文线索，在不同文明多维度全方位的视角下观察文物，并用深入浅出的语言进行解读，给人以精神层面的共鸣和享受。”这是她的粉丝给她总结的一大特点，也是她的魅力“之一”。</span></p><p style="line-height: normal;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></span></p></section></section></section></section></section></section></section><p><br/></p><p style="white-space: normal;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box; text-align: center;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(151, 124, 66); font-size: 14px;"></span></strong></p><p><br/></p></section></section></section><p><br/></p><section style="font-size: medium; white-space: normal; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; width: 7em; height: 7em; display: inline-block; vertical-align: bottom; border-radius: 100%; border-width: 5px; border-style: solid; box-shadow: rgb(204, 204, 204) 0.707107px 0.707107px 2px; border-color: white; background-position: center center; background-repeat: no-repeat; background-size: cover; background-image: url(&#39;http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appkHUDlT435887/image/ueditor/70884000_1538622842.cn/mmbiz_jpg/icetjwgztmpga7447pixc967w8a9raqjvth4vs7mraovyanz7jwgkglzzybjaqud4xr3h4ia8yuovwffu9tkduibw/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&#39;);"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 103.108px; height: 103.108px; overflow: hidden; box-sizing: border-box;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appkHUDlT435887/image/ueditor/81542900_1538622842.cn/mmbiz_jpg/icetjwgztmpga7447pixc967w8a9raqjvth4vs7mraovyanz7jwgkglzzybjaqud4xr3h4ia8yuovwffu9tkduibw/640" width="100%" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; height: 116.788px; width: 103.108px; opacity: 0; box-sizing: border-box;"/></section></section><section style="margin: -3em 0px 0px; padding: 0px 10px 10px; border-color: rgb(151, 124, 66); border-style: dotted; border-width: 2px; border-radius: 0.3em; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 3.5em 0px 15px; text-align: left; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;">冯海啸</span></strong></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;">资深文化艺术讲师</span></strong><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;"><br/></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box; text-align: center;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;"><strong style="font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: medium; text-align: center; white-space: normal; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box;">博物馆有得聊联合创始人</span></strong></span></strong></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;">2004年至今，曾长期担任拍卖公司书画部、古籍善本部业务经理，鉴定并征集齐白石《群虾图》、程十发《长吉诗意兰香神女图》、吴湖帆旧藏清汪由敦、钱维城书画合璧册页、秦权清拓本、唐海兽葡萄纹铜镜、明宣德青花缠枝莲纹折沿盆、明嘉靖五十四年项氏万卷堂刊本《前四史论赞》、明万历刊本《乡贤区西屏集》、明万历三年刻本《史记钞》、民国徐乃昌影刻明寒山赵均小宛堂本《玉台新咏》等重要文物。撰写并发表了《宋刻天禄琳琅藏本〈后村居士集〉》、《万古词章楮墨传——谈民国藏书家徐乃昌覆刻的明寒山赵氏小宛堂本〈玉台新咏〉》等文章。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;">2003年起至今，讲解各类展览20余个，为观众服务千余小时，并撰写多个展览的讲解词。</span></p><p><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;"><br/></span></p></section></section></section></section></section></section></section><section style="font-size: medium; white-space: normal; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"></section></section><p><br/></p><p style="white-space: normal;"><br/></p><p><br/></p>

第五讲：美食诱惑，古罗马遗址出土的银质餐具和汉朝的“小火锅”

https://fenxiao.xiaoe-tech.com/#/try_page/1/apphRvSiNoe4356/a_5c9219dec9c60_WWp4GrhL

<p><span style="font-size: 14px;"><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;">如果历史上没有秦汉与罗马，世界将会怎样？</span></strong><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;"></span></strong></span></p><p><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;">两千多年前，在欧亚大陆的东西两端出现了两个强大的国家：秦汉和罗马。它们代表着当时古代世界文明的最高辉煌成就。</span></p><p><span style="font-size: 14px;">&nbsp;</span></p><p><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;">英国著名历史学家汤因比在其《历史研究》一书中进行文明比较研究时，提出世界文明发展的两种主要模式，即希腊模式与中国模式。在他看来，古罗马文明是希腊模式高度发展的必然结果，所谓希腊文明亦可称为希腊—罗马文明，而中国的秦汉王朝则是中国模式的开始。</span></p><p><span style="font-size: 14px;">&nbsp;<img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appkHUDlT435887/image/ueditor/28035300_1538622915.jpg" title=".jpg" alt="幻灯片1.JPG"/></span></p><p><br/></p><p><span style="font-size: 14px;"><strong><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体;">这是一门欢迎碰撞，启发你思考的历史课</span></strong><strong><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体;"></span></strong></span></p><p><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;">《秦汉与罗马》专辑结合博物馆文物研究和遗址考古等热点，梳理对照两大文明政治、经济、文化及衣食住行生活的方方面面，不仅关注创造历史的大人物，更关心历史长河中的小人物等各阶层的生活。兼顾历史知识的架构和普及、艺术的审美及博物馆游学旅行的参考指南等功能。</span></p><p><span style="font-size: 14px;">&nbsp;<img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appkHUDlT435887/image/ueditor/21884400_1538622744.jpg" title=".jpg" alt="1 (2).JPG" style="font-size: 14px; white-space: normal;"/></span></p><p><span style="font-size: 14px;"><br/></span></p><p><span style="font-size: 14px;"><strong><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体;">本课程不同于你之前看过或听过的任何历史课</span></strong><strong><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体;"></span></strong></span></p><p><span style="font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体;">《秦汉与罗马》这个专辑与市场上的中国通史类音频课程最大的不同是</span><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;">: </span><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体;">将中国历史放入世界史的维度中看待。从全球史观的角度，通过同时期秦汉与罗马两大文明的对照，更清楚的看到中华文明的发展轨迹、与世界其它文明的碰撞和异同。</span><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;">&nbsp;</span></span></p><p><span style="font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;"><br/></span></p><p><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appkHUDlT435887/image/ueditor/47935400_1539331816.jpg" title=".jpg" alt="秦汉与罗马课程大纲.jpg"/></p><p><br/></p><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="text-align: center; margin: 10px 0% 20px; position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="display: inline-block; width: 47%; vertical-align: top; box-shadow: rgb(140, 140, 140) 0px 0px 3px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="display: inline-block; width: 100%; vertical-align: top; padding: 15px 10px 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;">你将获得</strong></p></section></section></section></section></section></section><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px 0% -10px; position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="max-width: 100%; vertical-align: middle; display: inline-block; box-shadow: rgb(0, 0, 0) 0px 0px 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appkHUDlT435887/image/ueditor/16838100_1538623070.png" style="vertical-align: middle; box-sizing: border-box;"/></section></section></section></section></section></section></section><p class="MsoListParagraph" style="margin-left: 24px"><span style="font-size: 14px;"></span></p><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 2; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">1.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong>中西文明溯源。</strong>精讲影响世界的两大文明，从源头梳理世界文明的发展，从各个角度相互对照，审视异同。使我们有机会观赏到两种不同历史背景下诞生和发展、且迥然各异的文化，感受漫漫历史长河中两大文明的璀璨和交融；</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">2.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong>一种看待历史的新角度。</strong>从我们的眼光看世界，从世界的眼光看自己，扩展眼界，拉开你和别人的认知差距；</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">3.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong>引发思考。</strong>破除非黑即白的观念，提升看待历史的格局，提高思辨能力，不人云亦云，启发独立思考；</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">4.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong>帮助你更清晰理解东西方思维模式及文明发展轨迹。</strong></p></section></section></section></section><p class="MsoListParagraph" style="margin-left: 24px"><br/></p><p><span style="font-size: 14px;">&nbsp;</span></p><p><span style="font-size: 14px;"><br/></span></p><p><span style="font-size: 14px;"><strong><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体;"></span></strong></span></p><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="text-align: center; margin: 10px 0% 20px; position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="display: inline-block; width: 47%; vertical-align: top; box-shadow: rgb(140, 140, 140) 0px 0px 3px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="display: inline-block; width: 100%; vertical-align: top; padding: 15px 10px 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;">适合谁听？</strong></p></section></section></section></section></section></section><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px 0% -10px; position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="max-width: 100%; vertical-align: middle; display: inline-block; box-shadow: rgb(0, 0, 0) 0px 0px 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appkHUDlT435887/image/ueditor/46571100_1538623092.png" style="vertical-align: middle; box-sizing: border-box;"/></section></section></section></section></section></section></section><p><span style="font-size: 14px;"><strong><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体;"></span></strong></span><br/></p><p class="MsoListParagraph" style="margin-left: 24px"><span style="font-size: 14px;"></span></p><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 2; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">1.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;常去博物馆，对秦汉及罗马文明历史、艺术感兴趣的朋友；</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">2.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;游走欧洲，想进一步了解欧洲文明发展的朋友；</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">3.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;关注历史，热爱人文、艺术的朋友；</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">4.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;不限于关注历史，更关心世界发展未来的朋友。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p></section></section></section></section><p class="MsoListParagraph" style="margin-left: 24px"><br/></p><section style="white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 10px 0px; text-align: center; position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="text-align: center; margin: 10px 0% 20px; position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="display: inline-block; width: 47%; vertical-align: top; box-shadow: rgb(140, 140, 140) 0px 0px 3px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="display: inline-block; width: 100%; vertical-align: top; padding: 15px 10px 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">主讲人</p></section></section></section></section></section></section><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px 0% -10px; position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="max-width: 100%; vertical-align: middle; display: inline-block; box-shadow: rgb(0, 0, 0) 0px 0px 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appkHUDlT435887/image/ueditor/70422700_1538623169.png" style="vertical-align: middle; box-sizing: border-box;"/></section></section></section></section></section></section></section><p><br/></p><p style="white-space: normal;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: center;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box;"></strong></span></strong></span></p><p style="white-space: normal;"><br/></p><p><br/></p><section style="font-size: medium; white-space: normal; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; width: 7em; height: 7em; display: inline-block; vertical-align: bottom; border-radius: 100%; border-width: 5px; border-style: solid; box-shadow: rgb(204, 204, 204) 0.707107px 0.707107px 2px; border-color: white; background-position: center center; background-repeat: no-repeat; background-size: cover; background-image: url(&#39;http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appkHUDlT435887/image/ueditor/15326300_1538623343.cn/mmbiz_jpg/icetjwgztmpez1lbsybfn6gkizfib5jnrmdly6zmae0fvzoa5ianeiyfgphmj5c6rv4pyctjkiat9hu2sjaxqad6qq/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&#39;);"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 103.108px; height: 103.108px; overflow: hidden; box-sizing: border-box;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appkHUDlT435887/image/ueditor/16014800_1538623343.cn/mmbiz_jpg/icetjwgztmpez1lbsybfn6gkizfib5jnrmdly6zmae0fvzoa5ianeiyfgphmj5c6rv4pyctjkiat9hu2sjaxqad6qq/640" width="100%" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; height: 122.448px; width: 103.108px; opacity: 0; box-sizing: border-box;"/></section></section><section style="margin: -3em 0px 0px; padding: 0px 10px 10px; border-color: rgb(151, 124, 66); border-style: dotted; border-width: 2px; border-radius: 0.3em; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 3.5em 0px 15px; text-align: left; line-height: 1.8; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box; line-height: normal;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box;">廖钒</span></strong></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box; line-height: normal;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box;">资深文化艺术讲师</span></strong></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box; line-height: normal;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box;">博物馆有得聊联合创始人</span></strong></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box; line-height: normal;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;"><br/></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box; line-height: normal;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;">做一件事情坚持超过15年的就该是真爱吧。从大学开始到现在，工作换了好几个，定期去博物馆一直没变过。</span><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box; line-height: normal;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box; line-height: normal;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;">她举办了近300场讲座。已为超过8万人讲解过国家博物馆15年来举办的50余个涵盖中外文明的展览。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box; line-height: normal;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box; line-height: normal;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box;">作为领队，她的准则是：讲之前，必须自己去过见过研究过。她自费考察了亚、欧、非20余个国家130多座城市的文化遗产、博物馆和古迹，直到现在，当她看到文艺复兴的雕塑作品，仍然心潮澎湃心动不已。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box; line-height: normal;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box;">“善于发现和抓住艺术背后的历史及人文线索，在不同文明多维度全方位的视角下观察文物，并用深入浅出的语言进行解读，给人以精神层面的共鸣和享受。”这是她的粉丝给她总结的一大特点，也是她的魅力“之一”。</span></p><p style="line-height: normal;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></span></p></section></section></section></section></section></section></section><p><br/></p><p style="white-space: normal;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box; text-align: center;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(151, 124, 66); font-size: 14px;"></span></strong></p><p><br/></p></section></section></section><p><br/></p><section style="font-size: medium; white-space: normal; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; width: 7em; height: 7em; display: inline-block; vertical-align: bottom; border-radius: 100%; border-width: 5px; border-style: solid; box-shadow: rgb(204, 204, 204) 0.707107px 0.707107px 2px; border-color: white; background-position: center center; background-repeat: no-repeat; background-size: cover; background-image: url(&#39;http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appkHUDlT435887/image/ueditor/70884000_1538622842.cn/mmbiz_jpg/icetjwgztmpga7447pixc967w8a9raqjvth4vs7mraovyanz7jwgkglzzybjaqud4xr3h4ia8yuovwffu9tkduibw/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&#39;);"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 103.108px; height: 103.108px; overflow: hidden; box-sizing: border-box;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appkHUDlT435887/image/ueditor/81542900_1538622842.cn/mmbiz_jpg/icetjwgztmpga7447pixc967w8a9raqjvth4vs7mraovyanz7jwgkglzzybjaqud4xr3h4ia8yuovwffu9tkduibw/640" width="100%" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; height: 116.788px; width: 103.108px; opacity: 0; box-sizing: border-box;"/></section></section><section style="margin: -3em 0px 0px; padding: 0px 10px 10px; border-color: rgb(151, 124, 66); border-style: dotted; border-width: 2px; border-radius: 0.3em; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 3.5em 0px 15px; text-align: left; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;">冯海啸</span></strong></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;">资深文化艺术讲师</span></strong><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;"><br/></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box; text-align: center;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;"><strong style="font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: medium; text-align: center; white-space: normal; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box;">博物馆有得聊联合创始人</span></strong></span></strong></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;">2004年至今，曾长期担任拍卖公司书画部、古籍善本部业务经理，鉴定并征集齐白石《群虾图》、程十发《长吉诗意兰香神女图》、吴湖帆旧藏清汪由敦、钱维城书画合璧册页、秦权清拓本、唐海兽葡萄纹铜镜、明宣德青花缠枝莲纹折沿盆、明嘉靖五十四年项氏万卷堂刊本《前四史论赞》、明万历刊本《乡贤区西屏集》、明万历三年刻本《史记钞》、民国徐乃昌影刻明寒山赵均小宛堂本《玉台新咏》等重要文物。撰写并发表了《宋刻天禄琳琅藏本〈后村居士集〉》、《万古词章楮墨传——谈民国藏书家徐乃昌覆刻的明寒山赵氏小宛堂本〈玉台新咏〉》等文章。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;">2003年起至今，讲解各类展览20余个，为观众服务千余小时，并撰写多个展览的讲解词。</span></p><p><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;"><br/></span></p></section></section></section></section></section></section></section><section style="font-size: medium; white-space: normal; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"></section></section><p><br/></p><p style="white-space: normal;"><br/></p><p><br/></p>

第六讲：被“定格”的民居，庞贝遗址农牧神之家和于庄汉墓陶建筑模型

https://fenxiao.xiaoe-tech.com/#/try_page/1/appHSU16PJe9200/a_5c9219dec9c1a_Nen7mjEh

<p><span style="font-size: 14px;"><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;">如果历史上没有秦汉与罗马，世界将会怎样？</span></strong><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;"></span></strong></span></p><p><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;">两千多年前，在欧亚大陆的东西两端出现了两个强大的国家：秦汉和罗马。它们代表着当时古代世界文明的最高辉煌成就。</span></p><p><span style="font-size: 14px;">&nbsp;</span></p><p><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;">英国著名历史学家汤因比在其《历史研究》一书中进行文明比较研究时，提出世界文明发展的两种主要模式，即希腊模式与中国模式。在他看来，古罗马文明是希腊模式高度发展的必然结果，所谓希腊文明亦可称为希腊—罗马文明，而中国的秦汉王朝则是中国模式的开始。</span></p><p><span style="font-size: 14px;">&nbsp;<img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appkHUDlT435887/image/ueditor/28035300_1538622915.jpg" title=".jpg" alt="幻灯片1.JPG"/></span></p><p><br/></p><p><span style="font-size: 14px;"><strong><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体;">这是一门欢迎碰撞，启发你思考的历史课</span></strong><strong><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体;"></span></strong></span></p><p><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;">《秦汉与罗马》专辑结合博物馆文物研究和遗址考古等热点，梳理对照两大文明政治、经济、文化及衣食住行生活的方方面面，不仅关注创造历史的大人物，更关心历史长河中的小人物等各阶层的生活。兼顾历史知识的架构和普及、艺术的审美及博物馆游学旅行的参考指南等功能。</span></p><p><span style="font-size: 14px;">&nbsp;<img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appkHUDlT435887/image/ueditor/21884400_1538622744.jpg" title=".jpg" alt="1 (2).JPG" style="font-size: 14px; white-space: normal;"/></span></p><p><span style="font-size: 14px;"><br/></span></p><p><span style="font-size: 14px;"><strong><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体;">本课程不同于你之前看过或听过的任何历史课</span></strong><strong><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体;"></span></strong></span></p><p><span style="font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体;">《秦汉与罗马》这个专辑与市场上的中国通史类音频课程最大的不同是</span><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;">: </span><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体;">将中国历史放入世界史的维度中看待。从全球史观的角度，通过同时期秦汉与罗马两大文明的对照，更清楚的看到中华文明的发展轨迹、与世界其它文明的碰撞和异同。</span><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;">&nbsp;</span></span></p><p><span style="font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;"><br/></span></p><p><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appkHUDlT435887/image/ueditor/47935400_1539331816.jpg" title=".jpg" alt="秦汉与罗马课程大纲.jpg"/></p><p><br/></p><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="text-align: center; margin: 10px 0% 20px; position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="display: inline-block; width: 47%; vertical-align: top; box-shadow: rgb(140, 140, 140) 0px 0px 3px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="display: inline-block; width: 100%; vertical-align: top; padding: 15px 10px 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;">你将获得</strong></p></section></section></section></section></section></section><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px 0% -10px; position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="max-width: 100%; vertical-align: middle; display: inline-block; box-shadow: rgb(0, 0, 0) 0px 0px 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appkHUDlT435887/image/ueditor/16838100_1538623070.png" style="vertical-align: middle; box-sizing: border-box;"/></section></section></section></section></section></section></section><p class="MsoListParagraph" style="margin-left: 24px"><span style="font-size: 14px;"></span></p><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 2; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">1.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong>中西文明溯源。</strong>精讲影响世界的两大文明，从源头梳理世界文明的发展，从各个角度相互对照，审视异同。使我们有机会观赏到两种不同历史背景下诞生和发展、且迥然各异的文化，感受漫漫历史长河中两大文明的璀璨和交融；</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">2.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong>一种看待历史的新角度。</strong>从我们的眼光看世界，从世界的眼光看自己，扩展眼界，拉开你和别人的认知差距；</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">3.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong>引发思考。</strong>破除非黑即白的观念，提升看待历史的格局，提高思辨能力，不人云亦云，启发独立思考；</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">4.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong>帮助你更清晰理解东西方思维模式及文明发展轨迹。</strong></p></section></section></section></section><p class="MsoListParagraph" style="margin-left: 24px"><br/></p><p><span style="font-size: 14px;">&nbsp;</span></p><p><span style="font-size: 14px;"><br/></span></p><p><span style="font-size: 14px;"><strong><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体;"></span></strong></span></p><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="text-align: center; margin: 10px 0% 20px; position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="display: inline-block; width: 47%; vertical-align: top; box-shadow: rgb(140, 140, 140) 0px 0px 3px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="display: inline-block; width: 100%; vertical-align: top; padding: 15px 10px 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;">适合谁听？</strong></p></section></section></section></section></section></section><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px 0% -10px; position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="max-width: 100%; vertical-align: middle; display: inline-block; box-shadow: rgb(0, 0, 0) 0px 0px 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appkHUDlT435887/image/ueditor/46571100_1538623092.png" style="vertical-align: middle; box-sizing: border-box;"/></section></section></section></section></section></section></section><p><span style="font-size: 14px;"><strong><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体;"></span></strong></span><br/></p><p class="MsoListParagraph" style="margin-left: 24px"><span style="font-size: 14px;"></span></p><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 2; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">1.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;常去博物馆，对秦汉及罗马文明历史、艺术感兴趣的朋友；</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">2.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;游走欧洲，想进一步了解欧洲文明发展的朋友；</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">3.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;关注历史，热爱人文、艺术的朋友；</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">4.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;不限于关注历史，更关心世界发展未来的朋友。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p></section></section></section></section><p class="MsoListParagraph" style="margin-left: 24px"><br/></p><section style="white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 10px 0px; text-align: center; position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="text-align: center; margin: 10px 0% 20px; position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="display: inline-block; width: 47%; vertical-align: top; box-shadow: rgb(140, 140, 140) 0px 0px 3px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="display: inline-block; width: 100%; vertical-align: top; padding: 15px 10px 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">主讲人</p></section></section></section></section></section></section><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px 0% -10px; position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="max-width: 100%; vertical-align: middle; display: inline-block; box-shadow: rgb(0, 0, 0) 0px 0px 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appkHUDlT435887/image/ueditor/70422700_1538623169.png" style="vertical-align: middle; box-sizing: border-box;"/></section></section></section></section></section></section></section><p><br/></p><p style="white-space: normal;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: center;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box;"></strong></span></strong></span></p><p style="white-space: normal;"><br/></p><p><br/></p><section style="font-size: medium; white-space: normal; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; width: 7em; height: 7em; display: inline-block; vertical-align: bottom; border-radius: 100%; border-width: 5px; border-style: solid; box-shadow: rgb(204, 204, 204) 0.707107px 0.707107px 2px; border-color: white; background-position: center center; background-repeat: no-repeat; background-size: cover; background-image: url(&#39;http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appkHUDlT435887/image/ueditor/15326300_1538623343.cn/mmbiz_jpg/icetjwgztmpez1lbsybfn6gkizfib5jnrmdly6zmae0fvzoa5ianeiyfgphmj5c6rv4pyctjkiat9hu2sjaxqad6qq/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&#39;);"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 103.108px; height: 103.108px; overflow: hidden; box-sizing: border-box;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appkHUDlT435887/image/ueditor/16014800_1538623343.cn/mmbiz_jpg/icetjwgztmpez1lbsybfn6gkizfib5jnrmdly6zmae0fvzoa5ianeiyfgphmj5c6rv4pyctjkiat9hu2sjaxqad6qq/640" width="100%" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; height: 122.448px; width: 103.108px; opacity: 0; box-sizing: border-box;"/></section></section><section style="margin: -3em 0px 0px; padding: 0px 10px 10px; border-color: rgb(151, 124, 66); border-style: dotted; border-width: 2px; border-radius: 0.3em; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 3.5em 0px 15px; text-align: left; line-height: 1.8; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box; line-height: normal;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box;">廖钒</span></strong></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box; line-height: normal;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box;">资深文化艺术讲师</span></strong></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box; line-height: normal;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box;">博物馆有得聊联合创始人</span></strong></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box; line-height: normal;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;"><br/></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box; line-height: normal;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;">做一件事情坚持超过15年的就该是真爱吧。从大学开始到现在，工作换了好几个，定期去博物馆一直没变过。</span><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box; line-height: normal;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box; line-height: normal;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;">她举办了近300场讲座。已为超过8万人讲解过国家博物馆15年来举办的50余个涵盖中外文明的展览。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box; line-height: normal;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box; line-height: normal;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box;">作为领队，她的准则是：讲之前，必须自己去过见过研究过。她自费考察了亚、欧、非20余个国家130多座城市的文化遗产、博物馆和古迹，直到现在，当她看到文艺复兴的雕塑作品，仍然心潮澎湃心动不已。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box; line-height: normal;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box;">“善于发现和抓住艺术背后的历史及人文线索，在不同文明多维度全方位的视角下观察文物，并用深入浅出的语言进行解读，给人以精神层面的共鸣和享受。”这是她的粉丝给她总结的一大特点，也是她的魅力“之一”。</span></p><p style="line-height: normal;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></span></p></section></section></section></section></section></section></section><p><br/></p><p style="white-space: normal;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box; text-align: center;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(151, 124, 66); font-size: 14px;"></span></strong></p><p><br/></p></section></section></section><p><br/></p><section style="font-size: medium; white-space: normal; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; width: 7em; height: 7em; display: inline-block; vertical-align: bottom; border-radius: 100%; border-width: 5px; border-style: solid; box-shadow: rgb(204, 204, 204) 0.707107px 0.707107px 2px; border-color: white; background-position: center center; background-repeat: no-repeat; background-size: cover; background-image: url(&#39;http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appkHUDlT435887/image/ueditor/70884000_1538622842.cn/mmbiz_jpg/icetjwgztmpga7447pixc967w8a9raqjvth4vs7mraovyanz7jwgkglzzybjaqud4xr3h4ia8yuovwffu9tkduibw/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&#39;);"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 103.108px; height: 103.108px; overflow: hidden; box-sizing: border-box;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appkHUDlT435887/image/ueditor/81542900_1538622842.cn/mmbiz_jpg/icetjwgztmpga7447pixc967w8a9raqjvth4vs7mraovyanz7jwgkglzzybjaqud4xr3h4ia8yuovwffu9tkduibw/640" width="100%" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; height: 116.788px; width: 103.108px; opacity: 0; box-sizing: border-box;"/></section></section><section style="margin: -3em 0px 0px; padding: 0px 10px 10px; border-color: rgb(151, 124, 66); border-style: dotted; border-width: 2px; border-radius: 0.3em; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 3.5em 0px 15px; text-align: left; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;">冯海啸</span></strong></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;">资深文化艺术讲师</span></strong><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;"><br/></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box; text-align: center;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;"><strong style="font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: medium; text-align: center; white-space: normal; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box;">博物馆有得聊联合创始人</span></strong></span></strong></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;">2004年至今，曾长期担任拍卖公司书画部、古籍善本部业务经理，鉴定并征集齐白石《群虾图》、程十发《长吉诗意兰香神女图》、吴湖帆旧藏清汪由敦、钱维城书画合璧册页、秦权清拓本、唐海兽葡萄纹铜镜、明宣德青花缠枝莲纹折沿盆、明嘉靖五十四年项氏万卷堂刊本《前四史论赞》、明万历刊本《乡贤区西屏集》、明万历三年刻本《史记钞》、民国徐乃昌影刻明寒山赵均小宛堂本《玉台新咏》等重要文物。撰写并发表了《宋刻天禄琳琅藏本〈后村居士集〉》、《万古词章楮墨传——谈民国藏书家徐乃昌覆刻的明寒山赵氏小宛堂本〈玉台新咏〉》等文章。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;">2003年起至今，讲解各类展览20余个，为观众服务千余小时，并撰写多个展览的讲解词。</span></p><p><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;"><br/></span></p></section></section></section></section></section></section></section><section style="font-size: medium; white-space: normal; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"></section></section><p><br/></p><p style="white-space: normal;"><br/></p><p><br/></p>

第七讲：对远方的追求，阿庇亚大道和秦驰道

https://fenxiao.xiaoe-tech.com/#/try_page/1/appHSU16PJe9200/a_5c9219dec9bce_ZEsLKZbN

<p><span style="font-size: 14px;"><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;">如果历史上没有秦汉与罗马，世界将会怎样？</span></strong><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;"></span></strong></span></p><p><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;">两千多年前，在欧亚大陆的东西两端出现了两个强大的国家：秦汉和罗马。它们代表着当时古代世界文明的最高辉煌成就。</span></p><p><span style="font-size: 14px;">&nbsp;</span></p><p><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;">英国著名历史学家汤因比在其《历史研究》一书中进行文明比较研究时，提出世界文明发展的两种主要模式，即希腊模式与中国模式。在他看来，古罗马文明是希腊模式高度发展的必然结果，所谓希腊文明亦可称为希腊—罗马文明，而中国的秦汉王朝则是中国模式的开始。</span></p><p><span style="font-size: 14px;">&nbsp;<img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appkHUDlT435887/image/ueditor/28035300_1538622915.jpg" title=".jpg" alt="幻灯片1.JPG"/></span></p><p><br/></p><p><span style="font-size: 14px;"><strong><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体;">这是一门欢迎碰撞，启发你思考的历史课</span></strong><strong><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体;"></span></strong></span></p><p><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;">《秦汉与罗马》专辑结合博物馆文物研究和遗址考古等热点，梳理对照两大文明政治、经济、文化及衣食住行生活的方方面面，不仅关注创造历史的大人物，更关心历史长河中的小人物等各阶层的生活。兼顾历史知识的架构和普及、艺术的审美及博物馆游学旅行的参考指南等功能。</span></p><p><span style="font-size: 14px;">&nbsp;<img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appkHUDlT435887/image/ueditor/21884400_1538622744.jpg" title=".jpg" alt="1 (2).JPG" style="font-size: 14px; white-space: normal;"/></span></p><p><span style="font-size: 14px;"><br/></span></p><p><span style="font-size: 14px;"><strong><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体;">本课程不同于你之前看过或听过的任何历史课</span></strong><strong><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体;"></span></strong></span></p><p><span style="font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体;">《秦汉与罗马》这个专辑与市场上的中国通史类音频课程最大的不同是</span><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;">: </span><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体;">将中国历史放入世界史的维度中看待。从全球史观的角度，通过同时期秦汉与罗马两大文明的对照，更清楚的看到中华文明的发展轨迹、与世界其它文明的碰撞和异同。</span><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;">&nbsp;</span></span></p><p><span style="font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;"><br/></span></p><p><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appkHUDlT435887/image/ueditor/47935400_1539331816.jpg" title=".jpg" alt="秦汉与罗马课程大纲.jpg"/></p><p><br/></p><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="text-align: center; margin: 10px 0% 20px; position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="display: inline-block; width: 47%; vertical-align: top; box-shadow: rgb(140, 140, 140) 0px 0px 3px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="display: inline-block; width: 100%; vertical-align: top; padding: 15px 10px 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;">你将获得</strong></p></section></section></section></section></section></section><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px 0% -10px; position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="max-width: 100%; vertical-align: middle; display: inline-block; box-shadow: rgb(0, 0, 0) 0px 0px 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appkHUDlT435887/image/ueditor/16838100_1538623070.png" style="vertical-align: middle; box-sizing: border-box;"/></section></section></section></section></section></section></section><p class="MsoListParagraph" style="margin-left: 24px"><span style="font-size: 14px;"></span></p><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 2; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">1.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong>中西文明溯源。</strong>精讲影响世界的两大文明，从源头梳理世界文明的发展，从各个角度相互对照，审视异同。使我们有机会观赏到两种不同历史背景下诞生和发展、且迥然各异的文化，感受漫漫历史长河中两大文明的璀璨和交融；</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">2.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong>一种看待历史的新角度。</strong>从我们的眼光看世界，从世界的眼光看自己，扩展眼界，拉开你和别人的认知差距；</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">3.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong>引发思考。</strong>破除非黑即白的观念，提升看待历史的格局，提高思辨能力，不人云亦云，启发独立思考；</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">4.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong>帮助你更清晰理解东西方思维模式及文明发展轨迹。</strong></p></section></section></section></section><p class="MsoListParagraph" style="margin-left: 24px"><br/></p><p><span style="font-size: 14px;">&nbsp;</span></p><p><span style="font-size: 14px;"><br/></span></p><p><span style="font-size: 14px;"><strong><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体;"></span></strong></span></p><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="text-align: center; margin: 10px 0% 20px; position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="display: inline-block; width: 47%; vertical-align: top; box-shadow: rgb(140, 140, 140) 0px 0px 3px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="display: inline-block; width: 100%; vertical-align: top; padding: 15px 10px 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;">适合谁听？</strong></p></section></section></section></section></section></section><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px 0% -10px; position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="max-width: 100%; vertical-align: middle; display: inline-block; box-shadow: rgb(0, 0, 0) 0px 0px 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appkHUDlT435887/image/ueditor/46571100_1538623092.png" style="vertical-align: middle; box-sizing: border-box;"/></section></section></section></section></section></section></section><p><span style="font-size: 14px;"><strong><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体;"></span></strong></span><br/></p><p class="MsoListParagraph" style="margin-left: 24px"><span style="font-size: 14px;"></span></p><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 2; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">1.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;常去博物馆，对秦汉及罗马文明历史、艺术感兴趣的朋友；</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">2.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;游走欧洲，想进一步了解欧洲文明发展的朋友；</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">3.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;关注历史，热爱人文、艺术的朋友；</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">4.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;不限于关注历史，更关心世界发展未来的朋友。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p></section></section></section></section><p class="MsoListParagraph" style="margin-left: 24px"><br/></p><section style="white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 10px 0px; text-align: center; position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="text-align: center; margin: 10px 0% 20px; position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="display: inline-block; width: 47%; vertical-align: top; box-shadow: rgb(140, 140, 140) 0px 0px 3px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="display: inline-block; width: 100%; vertical-align: top; padding: 15px 10px 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">主讲人</p></section></section></section></section></section></section><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px 0% -10px; position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="max-width: 100%; vertical-align: middle; display: inline-block; box-shadow: rgb(0, 0, 0) 0px 0px 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appkHUDlT435887/image/ueditor/70422700_1538623169.png" style="vertical-align: middle; box-sizing: border-box;"/></section></section></section></section></section></section></section><p><br/></p><p style="white-space: normal;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: center;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box;"></strong></span></strong></span></p><p style="white-space: normal;"><br/></p><p><br/></p><section style="font-size: medium; white-space: normal; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; width: 7em; height: 7em; display: inline-block; vertical-align: bottom; border-radius: 100%; border-width: 5px; border-style: solid; box-shadow: rgb(204, 204, 204) 0.707107px 0.707107px 2px; border-color: white; background-position: center center; background-repeat: no-repeat; background-size: cover; background-image: url(&#39;http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appkHUDlT435887/image/ueditor/15326300_1538623343.cn/mmbiz_jpg/icetjwgztmpez1lbsybfn6gkizfib5jnrmdly6zmae0fvzoa5ianeiyfgphmj5c6rv4pyctjkiat9hu2sjaxqad6qq/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&#39;);"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 103.108px; height: 103.108px; overflow: hidden; box-sizing: border-box;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appkHUDlT435887/image/ueditor/16014800_1538623343.cn/mmbiz_jpg/icetjwgztmpez1lbsybfn6gkizfib5jnrmdly6zmae0fvzoa5ianeiyfgphmj5c6rv4pyctjkiat9hu2sjaxqad6qq/640" width="100%" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; height: 122.448px; width: 103.108px; opacity: 0; box-sizing: border-box;"/></section></section><section style="margin: -3em 0px 0px; padding: 0px 10px 10px; border-color: rgb(151, 124, 66); border-style: dotted; border-width: 2px; border-radius: 0.3em; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 3.5em 0px 15px; text-align: left; line-height: 1.8; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box; line-height: normal;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box;">廖钒</span></strong></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box; line-height: normal;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box;">资深文化艺术讲师</span></strong></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box; line-height: normal;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box;">博物馆有得聊联合创始人</span></strong></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box; line-height: normal;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;"><br/></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box; line-height: normal;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;">做一件事情坚持超过15年的就该是真爱吧。从大学开始到现在，工作换了好几个，定期去博物馆一直没变过。</span><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box; line-height: normal;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box; line-height: normal;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;">她举办了近300场讲座。已为超过8万人讲解过国家博物馆15年来举办的50余个涵盖中外文明的展览。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box; line-height: normal;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box; line-height: normal;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box;">作为领队，她的准则是：讲之前，必须自己去过见过研究过。她自费考察了亚、欧、非20余个国家130多座城市的文化遗产、博物馆和古迹，直到现在，当她看到文艺复兴的雕塑作品，仍然心潮澎湃心动不已。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box; line-height: normal;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box;">“善于发现和抓住艺术背后的历史及人文线索，在不同文明多维度全方位的视角下观察文物，并用深入浅出的语言进行解读，给人以精神层面的共鸣和享受。”这是她的粉丝给她总结的一大特点，也是她的魅力“之一”。</span></p><p style="line-height: normal;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></span></p></section></section></section></section></section></section></section><p><br/></p><p style="white-space: normal;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box; text-align: center;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(151, 124, 66); font-size: 14px;"></span></strong></p><p><br/></p></section></section></section><p><br/></p><section style="font-size: medium; white-space: normal; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; width: 7em; height: 7em; display: inline-block; vertical-align: bottom; border-radius: 100%; border-width: 5px; border-style: solid; box-shadow: rgb(204, 204, 204) 0.707107px 0.707107px 2px; border-color: white; background-position: center center; background-repeat: no-repeat; background-size: cover; background-image: url(&#39;http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appkHUDlT435887/image/ueditor/70884000_1538622842.cn/mmbiz_jpg/icetjwgztmpga7447pixc967w8a9raqjvth4vs7mraovyanz7jwgkglzzybjaqud4xr3h4ia8yuovwffu9tkduibw/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&#39;);"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 103.108px; height: 103.108px; overflow: hidden; box-sizing: border-box;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appkHUDlT435887/image/ueditor/81542900_1538622842.cn/mmbiz_jpg/icetjwgztmpga7447pixc967w8a9raqjvth4vs7mraovyanz7jwgkglzzybjaqud4xr3h4ia8yuovwffu9tkduibw/640" width="100%" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; height: 116.788px; width: 103.108px; opacity: 0; box-sizing: border-box;"/></section></section><section style="margin: -3em 0px 0px; padding: 0px 10px 10px; border-color: rgb(151, 124, 66); border-style: dotted; border-width: 2px; border-radius: 0.3em; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 3.5em 0px 15px; text-align: left; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;">冯海啸</span></strong></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;">资深文化艺术讲师</span></strong><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;"><br/></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box; text-align: center;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;"><strong style="font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: medium; text-align: center; white-space: normal; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box;">博物馆有得聊联合创始人</span></strong></span></strong></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;">2004年至今，曾长期担任拍卖公司书画部、古籍善本部业务经理，鉴定并征集齐白石《群虾图》、程十发《长吉诗意兰香神女图》、吴湖帆旧藏清汪由敦、钱维城书画合璧册页、秦权清拓本、唐海兽葡萄纹铜镜、明宣德青花缠枝莲纹折沿盆、明嘉靖五十四年项氏万卷堂刊本《前四史论赞》、明万历刊本《乡贤区西屏集》、明万历三年刻本《史记钞》、民国徐乃昌影刻明寒山赵均小宛堂本《玉台新咏》等重要文物。撰写并发表了《宋刻天禄琳琅藏本〈后村居士集〉》、《万古词章楮墨传——谈民国藏书家徐乃昌覆刻的明寒山赵氏小宛堂本〈玉台新咏〉》等文章。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;">2003年起至今，讲解各类展览20余个，为观众服务千余小时，并撰写多个展览的讲解词。</span></p><p><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;"><br/></span></p></section></section></section></section></section></section></section><section style="font-size: medium; white-space: normal; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"></section></section><p><br/></p><p style="white-space: normal;"><br/></p><p><br/></p>

第八讲：死生本大事，满城汉墓金缕玉衣与库麦古墓室

https://fenxiao.xiaoe-tech.com/#/try_page/1/appHTQ2vlqX6470/a_5c9219dec9b87_J1ydI4BH

<p><span style="font-size: 14px;"><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;">如果历史上没有秦汉与罗马，世界将会怎样？</span></strong><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;"></span></strong></span></p><p><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;">两千多年前，在欧亚大陆的东西两端出现了两个强大的国家：秦汉和罗马。它们代表着当时古代世界文明的最高辉煌成就。</span></p><p><span style="font-size: 14px;">&nbsp;</span></p><p><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;">英国著名历史学家汤因比在其《历史研究》一书中进行文明比较研究时，提出世界文明发展的两种主要模式，即希腊模式与中国模式。在他看来，古罗马文明是希腊模式高度发展的必然结果，所谓希腊文明亦可称为希腊—罗马文明，而中国的秦汉王朝则是中国模式的开始。</span></p><p><span style="font-size: 14px;">&nbsp;<img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appkHUDlT435887/image/ueditor/28035300_1538622915.jpg" title=".jpg" alt="幻灯片1.JPG"/></span></p><p><br/></p><p><span style="font-size: 14px;"><strong><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体;">这是一门欢迎碰撞，启发你思考的历史课</span></strong><strong><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体;"></span></strong></span></p><p><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;">《秦汉与罗马》专辑结合博物馆文物研究和遗址考古等热点，梳理对照两大文明政治、经济、文化及衣食住行生活的方方面面，不仅关注创造历史的大人物，更关心历史长河中的小人物等各阶层的生活。兼顾历史知识的架构和普及、艺术的审美及博物馆游学旅行的参考指南等功能。</span></p><p><span style="font-size: 14px;">&nbsp;<img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appkHUDlT435887/image/ueditor/21884400_1538622744.jpg" title=".jpg" alt="1 (2).JPG" style="font-size: 14px; white-space: normal;"/></span></p><p><span style="font-size: 14px;"><br/></span></p><p><span style="font-size: 14px;"><strong><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体;">本课程不同于你之前看过或听过的任何历史课</span></strong><strong><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体;"></span></strong></span></p><p><span style="font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体;">《秦汉与罗马》这个专辑与市场上的中国通史类音频课程最大的不同是</span><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;">: </span><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体;">将中国历史放入世界史的维度中看待。从全球史观的角度，通过同时期秦汉与罗马两大文明的对照，更清楚的看到中华文明的发展轨迹、与世界其它文明的碰撞和异同。</span><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;">&nbsp;</span></span></p><p><span style="font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;"><br/></span></p><p><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appkHUDlT435887/image/ueditor/47935400_1539331816.jpg" title=".jpg" alt="秦汉与罗马课程大纲.jpg"/></p><p><br/></p><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="text-align: center; margin: 10px 0% 20px; position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="display: inline-block; width: 47%; vertical-align: top; box-shadow: rgb(140, 140, 140) 0px 0px 3px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="display: inline-block; width: 100%; vertical-align: top; padding: 15px 10px 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;">你将获得</strong></p></section></section></section></section></section></section><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px 0% -10px; position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="max-width: 100%; vertical-align: middle; display: inline-block; box-shadow: rgb(0, 0, 0) 0px 0px 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appkHUDlT435887/image/ueditor/16838100_1538623070.png" style="vertical-align: middle; box-sizing: border-box;"/></section></section></section></section></section></section></section><p class="MsoListParagraph" style="margin-left: 24px"><span style="font-size: 14px;"></span></p><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 2; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">1.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong>中西文明溯源。</strong>精讲影响世界的两大文明，从源头梳理世界文明的发展，从各个角度相互对照，审视异同。使我们有机会观赏到两种不同历史背景下诞生和发展、且迥然各异的文化，感受漫漫历史长河中两大文明的璀璨和交融；</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">2.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong>一种看待历史的新角度。</strong>从我们的眼光看世界，从世界的眼光看自己，扩展眼界，拉开你和别人的认知差距；</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">3.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong>引发思考。</strong>破除非黑即白的观念，提升看待历史的格局，提高思辨能力，不人云亦云，启发独立思考；</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">4.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong>帮助你更清晰理解东西方思维模式及文明发展轨迹。</strong></p></section></section></section></section><p class="MsoListParagraph" style="margin-left: 24px"><br/></p><p><span style="font-size: 14px;">&nbsp;</span></p><p><span style="font-size: 14px;"><br/></span></p><p><span style="font-size: 14px;"><strong><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体;"></span></strong></span></p><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="text-align: center; margin: 10px 0% 20px; position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="display: inline-block; width: 47%; vertical-align: top; box-shadow: rgb(140, 140, 140) 0px 0px 3px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="display: inline-block; width: 100%; vertical-align: top; padding: 15px 10px 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;">适合谁听？</strong></p></section></section></section></section></section></section><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px 0% -10px; position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="max-width: 100%; vertical-align: middle; display: inline-block; box-shadow: rgb(0, 0, 0) 0px 0px 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appkHUDlT435887/image/ueditor/46571100_1538623092.png" style="vertical-align: middle; box-sizing: border-box;"/></section></section></section></section></section></section></section><p><span style="font-size: 14px;"><strong><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体;"></span></strong></span><br/></p><p class="MsoListParagraph" style="margin-left: 24px"><span style="font-size: 14px;"></span></p><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 2; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">1.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;常去博物馆，对秦汉及罗马文明历史、艺术感兴趣的朋友；</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">2.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;游走欧洲，想进一步了解欧洲文明发展的朋友；</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">3.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;关注历史，热爱人文、艺术的朋友；</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">4.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;不限于关注历史，更关心世界发展未来的朋友。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p></section></section></section></section><p class="MsoListParagraph" style="margin-left: 24px"><br/></p><section style="white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 10px 0px; text-align: center; position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="text-align: center; margin: 10px 0% 20px; position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="display: inline-block; width: 47%; vertical-align: top; box-shadow: rgb(140, 140, 140) 0px 0px 3px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="display: inline-block; width: 100%; vertical-align: top; padding: 15px 10px 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">主讲人</p></section></section></section></section></section></section><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px 0% -10px; position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="max-width: 100%; vertical-align: middle; display: inline-block; box-shadow: rgb(0, 0, 0) 0px 0px 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appkHUDlT435887/image/ueditor/70422700_1538623169.png" style="vertical-align: middle; box-sizing: border-box;"/></section></section></section></section></section></section></section><p><br/></p><p style="white-space: normal;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: center;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box;"></strong></span></strong></span></p><p style="white-space: normal;"><br/></p><p><br/></p><section style="font-size: medium; white-space: normal; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; width: 7em; height: 7em; display: inline-block; vertical-align: bottom; border-radius: 100%; border-width: 5px; border-style: solid; box-shadow: rgb(204, 204, 204) 0.707107px 0.707107px 2px; border-color: white; background-position: center center; background-repeat: no-repeat; background-size: cover; background-image: url(&#39;http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appkHUDlT435887/image/ueditor/15326300_1538623343.cn/mmbiz_jpg/icetjwgztmpez1lbsybfn6gkizfib5jnrmdly6zmae0fvzoa5ianeiyfgphmj5c6rv4pyctjkiat9hu2sjaxqad6qq/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&#39;);"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 103.108px; height: 103.108px; overflow: hidden; box-sizing: border-box;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appkHUDlT435887/image/ueditor/16014800_1538623343.cn/mmbiz_jpg/icetjwgztmpez1lbsybfn6gkizfib5jnrmdly6zmae0fvzoa5ianeiyfgphmj5c6rv4pyctjkiat9hu2sjaxqad6qq/640" width="100%" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; height: 122.448px; width: 103.108px; opacity: 0; box-sizing: border-box;"/></section></section><section style="margin: -3em 0px 0px; padding: 0px 10px 10px; border-color: rgb(151, 124, 66); border-style: dotted; border-width: 2px; border-radius: 0.3em; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 3.5em 0px 15px; text-align: left; line-height: 1.8; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box; line-height: normal;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box;">廖钒</span></strong></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box; line-height: normal;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box;">资深文化艺术讲师</span></strong></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box; line-height: normal;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box;">博物馆有得聊联合创始人</span></strong></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box; line-height: normal;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;"><br/></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box; line-height: normal;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;">做一件事情坚持超过15年的就该是真爱吧。从大学开始到现在，工作换了好几个，定期去博物馆一直没变过。</span><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box; line-height: normal;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box; line-height: normal;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;">她举办了近300场讲座。已为超过8万人讲解过国家博物馆15年来举办的50余个涵盖中外文明的展览。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box; line-height: normal;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box; line-height: normal;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box;">作为领队，她的准则是：讲之前，必须自己去过见过研究过。她自费考察了亚、欧、非20余个国家130多座城市的文化遗产、博物馆和古迹，直到现在，当她看到文艺复兴的雕塑作品，仍然心潮澎湃心动不已。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box; line-height: normal;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box;">“善于发现和抓住艺术背后的历史及人文线索，在不同文明多维度全方位的视角下观察文物，并用深入浅出的语言进行解读，给人以精神层面的共鸣和享受。”这是她的粉丝给她总结的一大特点，也是她的魅力“之一”。</span></p><p style="line-height: normal;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></span></p></section></section></section></section></section></section></section><p><br/></p><p style="white-space: normal;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box; text-align: center;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(151, 124, 66); font-size: 14px;"></span></strong></p><p><br/></p></section></section></section><p><br/></p><section style="font-size: medium; white-space: normal; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; width: 7em; height: 7em; display: inline-block; vertical-align: bottom; border-radius: 100%; border-width: 5px; border-style: solid; box-shadow: rgb(204, 204, 204) 0.707107px 0.707107px 2px; border-color: white; background-position: center center; background-repeat: no-repeat; background-size: cover; background-image: url(&#39;http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appkHUDlT435887/image/ueditor/70884000_1538622842.cn/mmbiz_jpg/icetjwgztmpga7447pixc967w8a9raqjvth4vs7mraovyanz7jwgkglzzybjaqud4xr3h4ia8yuovwffu9tkduibw/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&#39;);"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 103.108px; height: 103.108px; overflow: hidden; box-sizing: border-box;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appkHUDlT435887/image/ueditor/81542900_1538622842.cn/mmbiz_jpg/icetjwgztmpga7447pixc967w8a9raqjvth4vs7mraovyanz7jwgkglzzybjaqud4xr3h4ia8yuovwffu9tkduibw/640" width="100%" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; height: 116.788px; width: 103.108px; opacity: 0; box-sizing: border-box;"/></section></section><section style="margin: -3em 0px 0px; padding: 0px 10px 10px; border-color: rgb(151, 124, 66); border-style: dotted; border-width: 2px; border-radius: 0.3em; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 3.5em 0px 15px; text-align: left; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;">冯海啸</span></strong></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;">资深文化艺术讲师</span></strong><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;"><br/></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box; text-align: center;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;"><strong style="font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: medium; text-align: center; white-space: normal; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box;">博物馆有得聊联合创始人</span></strong></span></strong></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;">2004年至今，曾长期担任拍卖公司书画部、古籍善本部业务经理，鉴定并征集齐白石《群虾图》、程十发《长吉诗意兰香神女图》、吴湖帆旧藏清汪由敦、钱维城书画合璧册页、秦权清拓本、唐海兽葡萄纹铜镜、明宣德青花缠枝莲纹折沿盆、明嘉靖五十四年项氏万卷堂刊本《前四史论赞》、明万历刊本《乡贤区西屏集》、明万历三年刻本《史记钞》、民国徐乃昌影刻明寒山赵均小宛堂本《玉台新咏》等重要文物。撰写并发表了《宋刻天禄琳琅藏本〈后村居士集〉》、《万古词章楮墨传——谈民国藏书家徐乃昌覆刻的明寒山赵氏小宛堂本〈玉台新咏〉》等文章。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;">2003年起至今，讲解各类展览20余个，为观众服务千余小时，并撰写多个展览的讲解词。</span></p><p><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;"><br/></span></p></section></section></section></section></section></section></section><section style="font-size: medium; white-space: normal; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"></section></section><p><br/></p><p style="white-space: normal;"><br/></p><p><br/></p>

第九讲：古来征战地，布匿战争与长平之战

https://fenxiao.xiaoe-tech.com/#/try_page/1/appHux28VQ81650/a_5c9219dec9b3e_nJcqqLRS

<p><span style="font-size: 14px;"><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;">如果历史上没有秦汉与罗马，世界将会怎样？</span></strong><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;"></span></strong></span></p><p><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;">两千多年前，在欧亚大陆的东西两端出现了两个强大的国家：秦汉和罗马。它们代表着当时古代世界文明的最高辉煌成就。</span></p><p><span style="font-size: 14px;">&nbsp;</span></p><p><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;">英国著名历史学家汤因比在其《历史研究》一书中进行文明比较研究时，提出世界文明发展的两种主要模式，即希腊模式与中国模式。在他看来，古罗马文明是希腊模式高度发展的必然结果，所谓希腊文明亦可称为希腊—罗马文明，而中国的秦汉王朝则是中国模式的开始。</span></p><p><span style="font-size: 14px;">&nbsp;<img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appkHUDlT435887/image/ueditor/28035300_1538622915.jpg" title=".jpg" alt="幻灯片1.JPG"/></span></p><p><br/></p><p><span style="font-size: 14px;"><strong><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体;">这是一门欢迎碰撞，启发你思考的历史课</span></strong><strong><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体;"></span></strong></span></p><p><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;">《秦汉与罗马》专辑结合博物馆文物研究和遗址考古等热点，梳理对照两大文明政治、经济、文化及衣食住行生活的方方面面，不仅关注创造历史的大人物，更关心历史长河中的小人物等各阶层的生活。兼顾历史知识的架构和普及、艺术的审美及博物馆游学旅行的参考指南等功能。</span></p><p><span style="font-size: 14px;">&nbsp;<img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appkHUDlT435887/image/ueditor/21884400_1538622744.jpg" title=".jpg" alt="1 (2).JPG" style="font-size: 14px; white-space: normal;"/></span></p><p><span style="font-size: 14px;"><br/></span></p><p><span style="font-size: 14px;"><strong><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体;">本课程不同于你之前看过或听过的任何历史课</span></strong><strong><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体;"></span></strong></span></p><p><span style="font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体;">《秦汉与罗马》这个专辑与市场上的中国通史类音频课程最大的不同是</span><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;">: </span><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体;">将中国历史放入世界史的维度中看待。从全球史观的角度，通过同时期秦汉与罗马两大文明的对照，更清楚的看到中华文明的发展轨迹、与世界其它文明的碰撞和异同。</span><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;">&nbsp;</span></span></p><p><span style="font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;"><br/></span></p><p><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appkHUDlT435887/image/ueditor/47935400_1539331816.jpg" title=".jpg" alt="秦汉与罗马课程大纲.jpg"/></p><p><br/></p><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="text-align: center; margin: 10px 0% 20px; position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="display: inline-block; width: 47%; vertical-align: top; box-shadow: rgb(140, 140, 140) 0px 0px 3px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="display: inline-block; width: 100%; vertical-align: top; padding: 15px 10px 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;">你将获得</strong></p></section></section></section></section></section></section><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px 0% -10px; position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="max-width: 100%; vertical-align: middle; display: inline-block; box-shadow: rgb(0, 0, 0) 0px 0px 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appkHUDlT435887/image/ueditor/16838100_1538623070.png" style="vertical-align: middle; box-sizing: border-box;"/></section></section></section></section></section></section></section><p class="MsoListParagraph" style="margin-left: 24px"><span style="font-size: 14px;"></span></p><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 2; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">1.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong>中西文明溯源。</strong>精讲影响世界的两大文明，从源头梳理世界文明的发展，从各个角度相互对照，审视异同。使我们有机会观赏到两种不同历史背景下诞生和发展、且迥然各异的文化，感受漫漫历史长河中两大文明的璀璨和交融；</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">2.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong>一种看待历史的新角度。</strong>从我们的眼光看世界，从世界的眼光看自己，扩展眼界，拉开你和别人的认知差距；</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">3.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong>引发思考。</strong>破除非黑即白的观念，提升看待历史的格局，提高思辨能力，不人云亦云，启发独立思考；</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">4.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong>帮助你更清晰理解东西方思维模式及文明发展轨迹。</strong></p></section></section></section></section><p class="MsoListParagraph" style="margin-left: 24px"><br/></p><p><span style="font-size: 14px;">&nbsp;</span></p><p><span style="font-size: 14px;"><br/></span></p><p><span style="font-size: 14px;"><strong><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体;"></span></strong></span></p><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="text-align: center; margin: 10px 0% 20px; position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="display: inline-block; width: 47%; vertical-align: top; box-shadow: rgb(140, 140, 140) 0px 0px 3px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="display: inline-block; width: 100%; vertical-align: top; padding: 15px 10px 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;">适合谁听？</strong></p></section></section></section></section></section></section><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px 0% -10px; position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="max-width: 100%; vertical-align: middle; display: inline-block; box-shadow: rgb(0, 0, 0) 0px 0px 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appkHUDlT435887/image/ueditor/46571100_1538623092.png" style="vertical-align: middle; box-sizing: border-box;"/></section></section></section></section></section></section></section><p><span style="font-size: 14px;"><strong><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体;"></span></strong></span><br/></p><p class="MsoListParagraph" style="margin-left: 24px"><span style="font-size: 14px;"></span></p><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 2; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">1.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;常去博物馆，对秦汉及罗马文明历史、艺术感兴趣的朋友；</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">2.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;游走欧洲，想进一步了解欧洲文明发展的朋友；</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">3.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;关注历史，热爱人文、艺术的朋友；</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">4.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;不限于关注历史，更关心世界发展未来的朋友。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p></section></section></section></section><p class="MsoListParagraph" style="margin-left: 24px"><br/></p><section style="white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 10px 0px; text-align: center; position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="text-align: center; margin: 10px 0% 20px; position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="display: inline-block; width: 47%; vertical-align: top; box-shadow: rgb(140, 140, 140) 0px 0px 3px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="display: inline-block; width: 100%; vertical-align: top; padding: 15px 10px 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">主讲人</p></section></section></section></section></section></section><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px 0% -10px; position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="max-width: 100%; vertical-align: middle; display: inline-block; box-shadow: rgb(0, 0, 0) 0px 0px 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appkHUDlT435887/image/ueditor/70422700_1538623169.png" style="vertical-align: middle; box-sizing: border-box;"/></section></section></section></section></section></section></section><p><br/></p><p style="white-space: normal;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: center;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box;"></strong></span></strong></span></p><p style="white-space: normal;"><br/></p><p><br/></p><section style="font-size: medium; white-space: normal; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; width: 7em; height: 7em; display: inline-block; vertical-align: bottom; border-radius: 100%; border-width: 5px; border-style: solid; box-shadow: rgb(204, 204, 204) 0.707107px 0.707107px 2px; border-color: white; background-position: center center; background-repeat: no-repeat; background-size: cover; background-image: url(&#39;http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appkHUDlT435887/image/ueditor/15326300_1538623343.cn/mmbiz_jpg/icetjwgztmpez1lbsybfn6gkizfib5jnrmdly6zmae0fvzoa5ianeiyfgphmj5c6rv4pyctjkiat9hu2sjaxqad6qq/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&#39;);"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 103.108px; height: 103.108px; overflow: hidden; box-sizing: border-box;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appkHUDlT435887/image/ueditor/16014800_1538623343.cn/mmbiz_jpg/icetjwgztmpez1lbsybfn6gkizfib5jnrmdly6zmae0fvzoa5ianeiyfgphmj5c6rv4pyctjkiat9hu2sjaxqad6qq/640" width="100%" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; height: 122.448px; width: 103.108px; opacity: 0; box-sizing: border-box;"/></section></section><section style="margin: -3em 0px 0px; padding: 0px 10px 10px; border-color: rgb(151, 124, 66); border-style: dotted; border-width: 2px; border-radius: 0.3em; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 3.5em 0px 15px; text-align: left; line-height: 1.8; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box; line-height: normal;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box;">廖钒</span></strong></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box; line-height: normal;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box;">资深文化艺术讲师</span></strong></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box; line-height: normal;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box;">博物馆有得聊联合创始人</span></strong></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box; line-height: normal;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;"><br/></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box; line-height: normal;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;">做一件事情坚持超过15年的就该是真爱吧。从大学开始到现在，工作换了好几个，定期去博物馆一直没变过。</span><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box; line-height: normal;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box; line-height: normal;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;">她举办了近300场讲座。已为超过8万人讲解过国家博物馆15年来举办的50余个涵盖中外文明的展览。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box; line-height: normal;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box; line-height: normal;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box;">作为领队，她的准则是：讲之前，必须自己去过见过研究过。她自费考察了亚、欧、非20余个国家130多座城市的文化遗产、博物馆和古迹，直到现在，当她看到文艺复兴的雕塑作品，仍然心潮澎湃心动不已。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box; line-height: normal;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box;">“善于发现和抓住艺术背后的历史及人文线索，在不同文明多维度全方位的视角下观察文物，并用深入浅出的语言进行解读，给人以精神层面的共鸣和享受。”这是她的粉丝给她总结的一大特点，也是她的魅力“之一”。</span></p><p style="line-height: normal;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></span></p></section></section></section></section></section></section></section><p><br/></p><p style="white-space: normal;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box; text-align: center;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(151, 124, 66); font-size: 14px;"></span></strong></p><p><br/></p></section></section></section><p><br/></p><section style="font-size: medium; white-space: normal; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; width: 7em; height: 7em; display: inline-block; vertical-align: bottom; border-radius: 100%; border-width: 5px; border-style: solid; box-shadow: rgb(204, 204, 204) 0.707107px 0.707107px 2px; border-color: white; background-position: center center; background-repeat: no-repeat; background-size: cover; background-image: url(&#39;http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appkHUDlT435887/image/ueditor/70884000_1538622842.cn/mmbiz_jpg/icetjwgztmpga7447pixc967w8a9raqjvth4vs7mraovyanz7jwgkglzzybjaqud4xr3h4ia8yuovwffu9tkduibw/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&#39;);"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 103.108px; height: 103.108px; overflow: hidden; box-sizing: border-box;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appkHUDlT435887/image/ueditor/81542900_1538622842.cn/mmbiz_jpg/icetjwgztmpga7447pixc967w8a9raqjvth4vs7mraovyanz7jwgkglzzybjaqud4xr3h4ia8yuovwffu9tkduibw/640" width="100%" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; height: 116.788px; width: 103.108px; opacity: 0; box-sizing: border-box;"/></section></section><section style="margin: -3em 0px 0px; padding: 0px 10px 10px; border-color: rgb(151, 124, 66); border-style: dotted; border-width: 2px; border-radius: 0.3em; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 3.5em 0px 15px; text-align: left; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;">冯海啸</span></strong></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;">资深文化艺术讲师</span></strong><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;"><br/></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box; text-align: center;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;"><strong style="font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: medium; text-align: center; white-space: normal; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box;">博物馆有得聊联合创始人</span></strong></span></strong></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;">2004年至今，曾长期担任拍卖公司书画部、古籍善本部业务经理，鉴定并征集齐白石《群虾图》、程十发《长吉诗意兰香神女图》、吴湖帆旧藏清汪由敦、钱维城书画合璧册页、秦权清拓本、唐海兽葡萄纹铜镜、明宣德青花缠枝莲纹折沿盆、明嘉靖五十四年项氏万卷堂刊本《前四史论赞》、明万历刊本《乡贤区西屏集》、明万历三年刻本《史记钞》、民国徐乃昌影刻明寒山赵均小宛堂本《玉台新咏》等重要文物。撰写并发表了《宋刻天禄琳琅藏本〈后村居士集〉》、《万古词章楮墨传——谈民国藏书家徐乃昌覆刻的明寒山赵氏小宛堂本〈玉台新咏〉》等文章。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;">2003年起至今，讲解各类展览20余个，为观众服务千余小时，并撰写多个展览的讲解词。</span></p><p><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;"><br/></span></p></section></section></section></section></section></section></section><section style="font-size: medium; white-space: normal; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"></section></section><p><br/></p><p style="white-space: normal;"><br/></p><p><br/></p>

第十讲：思你所想，卡拉卡拉浴场密特拉教洞穴和睡虎地秦简

https://fenxiao.xiaoe-tech.com/#/try_page/1/apphV5jcnuj3845/a_5c9219dec9ae6_jItzy4nS

<p><span style="font-size: 14px;"><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;">如果历史上没有秦汉与罗马，世界将会怎样？</span></strong><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;"></span></strong></span></p><p><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;">两千多年前，在欧亚大陆的东西两端出现了两个强大的国家：秦汉和罗马。它们代表着当时古代世界文明的最高辉煌成就。</span></p><p><span style="font-size: 14px;">&nbsp;</span></p><p><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;">英国著名历史学家汤因比在其《历史研究》一书中进行文明比较研究时，提出世界文明发展的两种主要模式，即希腊模式与中国模式。在他看来，古罗马文明是希腊模式高度发展的必然结果，所谓希腊文明亦可称为希腊—罗马文明，而中国的秦汉王朝则是中国模式的开始。</span></p><p><span style="font-size: 14px;">&nbsp;<img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appkHUDlT435887/image/ueditor/28035300_1538622915.jpg" title=".jpg" alt="幻灯片1.JPG"/></span></p><p><br/></p><p><span style="font-size: 14px;"><strong><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体;">这是一门欢迎碰撞，启发你思考的历史课</span></strong><strong><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体;"></span></strong></span></p><p><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;">《秦汉与罗马》专辑结合博物馆文物研究和遗址考古等热点，梳理对照两大文明政治、经济、文化及衣食住行生活的方方面面，不仅关注创造历史的大人物，更关心历史长河中的小人物等各阶层的生活。兼顾历史知识的架构和普及、艺术的审美及博物馆游学旅行的参考指南等功能。</span></p><p><span style="font-size: 14px;">&nbsp;<img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appkHUDlT435887/image/ueditor/21884400_1538622744.jpg" title=".jpg" alt="1 (2).JPG" style="font-size: 14px; white-space: normal;"/></span></p><p><span style="font-size: 14px;"><br/></span></p><p><span style="font-size: 14px;"><strong><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体;">本课程不同于你之前看过或听过的任何历史课</span></strong><strong><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体;"></span></strong></span></p><p><span style="font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体;">《秦汉与罗马》这个专辑与市场上的中国通史类音频课程最大的不同是</span><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;">: </span><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体;">将中国历史放入世界史的维度中看待。从全球史观的角度，通过同时期秦汉与罗马两大文明的对照，更清楚的看到中华文明的发展轨迹、与世界其它文明的碰撞和异同。</span><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;">&nbsp;</span></span></p><p><span style="font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;"><br/></span></p><p><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appkHUDlT435887/image/ueditor/47935400_1539331816.jpg" title=".jpg" alt="秦汉与罗马课程大纲.jpg"/></p><p><br/></p><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="text-align: center; margin: 10px 0% 20px; position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="display: inline-block; width: 47%; vertical-align: top; box-shadow: rgb(140, 140, 140) 0px 0px 3px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="display: inline-block; width: 100%; vertical-align: top; padding: 15px 10px 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;">你将获得</strong></p></section></section></section></section></section></section><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px 0% -10px; position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="max-width: 100%; vertical-align: middle; display: inline-block; box-shadow: rgb(0, 0, 0) 0px 0px 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appkHUDlT435887/image/ueditor/16838100_1538623070.png" style="vertical-align: middle; box-sizing: border-box;"/></section></section></section></section></section></section></section><p class="MsoListParagraph" style="margin-left: 24px"><span style="font-size: 14px;"></span></p><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 2; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">1.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong>中西文明溯源。</strong>精讲影响世界的两大文明，从源头梳理世界文明的发展，从各个角度相互对照，审视异同。使我们有机会观赏到两种不同历史背景下诞生和发展、且迥然各异的文化，感受漫漫历史长河中两大文明的璀璨和交融；</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">2.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong>一种看待历史的新角度。</strong>从我们的眼光看世界，从世界的眼光看自己，扩展眼界，拉开你和别人的认知差距；</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">3.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong>引发思考。</strong>破除非黑即白的观念，提升看待历史的格局，提高思辨能力，不人云亦云，启发独立思考；</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">4.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong>帮助你更清晰理解东西方思维模式及文明发展轨迹。</strong></p></section></section></section></section><p class="MsoListParagraph" style="margin-left: 24px"><br/></p><p><span style="font-size: 14px;">&nbsp;</span></p><p><span style="font-size: 14px;"><br/></span></p><p><span style="font-size: 14px;"><strong><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体;"></span></strong></span></p><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="text-align: center; margin: 10px 0% 20px; position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="display: inline-block; width: 47%; vertical-align: top; box-shadow: rgb(140, 140, 140) 0px 0px 3px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="display: inline-block; width: 100%; vertical-align: top; padding: 15px 10px 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;">适合谁听？</strong></p></section></section></section></section></section></section><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px 0% -10px; position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="max-width: 100%; vertical-align: middle; display: inline-block; box-shadow: rgb(0, 0, 0) 0px 0px 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appkHUDlT435887/image/ueditor/46571100_1538623092.png" style="vertical-align: middle; box-sizing: border-box;"/></section></section></section></section></section></section></section><p><span style="font-size: 14px;"><strong><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体;"></span></strong></span><br/></p><p class="MsoListParagraph" style="margin-left: 24px"><span style="font-size: 14px;"></span></p><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 2; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">1.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;常去博物馆，对秦汉及罗马文明历史、艺术感兴趣的朋友；</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">2.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;游走欧洲，想进一步了解欧洲文明发展的朋友；</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">3.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;关注历史，热爱人文、艺术的朋友；</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">4.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;不限于关注历史，更关心世界发展未来的朋友。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p></section></section></section></section><p class="MsoListParagraph" style="margin-left: 24px"><br/></p><section style="white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 10px 0px; text-align: center; position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="text-align: center; margin: 10px 0% 20px; position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="display: inline-block; width: 47%; vertical-align: top; box-shadow: rgb(140, 140, 140) 0px 0px 3px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="display: inline-block; width: 100%; vertical-align: top; padding: 15px 10px 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">主讲人</p></section></section></section></section></section></section><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px 0% -10px; position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="max-width: 100%; vertical-align: middle; display: inline-block; box-shadow: rgb(0, 0, 0) 0px 0px 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appkHUDlT435887/image/ueditor/70422700_1538623169.png" style="vertical-align: middle; box-sizing: border-box;"/></section></section></section></section></section></section></section><p><br/></p><p style="white-space: normal;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: center;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box;"></strong></span></strong></span></p><p style="white-space: normal;"><br/></p><p><br/></p><section style="font-size: medium; white-space: normal; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; width: 7em; height: 7em; display: inline-block; vertical-align: bottom; border-radius: 100%; border-width: 5px; border-style: solid; box-shadow: rgb(204, 204, 204) 0.707107px 0.707107px 2px; border-color: white; background-position: center center; background-repeat: no-repeat; background-size: cover; background-image: url(&#39;http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appkHUDlT435887/image/ueditor/15326300_1538623343.cn/mmbiz_jpg/icetjwgztmpez1lbsybfn6gkizfib5jnrmdly6zmae0fvzoa5ianeiyfgphmj5c6rv4pyctjkiat9hu2sjaxqad6qq/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&#39;);"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 103.108px; height: 103.108px; overflow: hidden; box-sizing: border-box;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appkHUDlT435887/image/ueditor/16014800_1538623343.cn/mmbiz_jpg/icetjwgztmpez1lbsybfn6gkizfib5jnrmdly6zmae0fvzoa5ianeiyfgphmj5c6rv4pyctjkiat9hu2sjaxqad6qq/640" width="100%" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; height: 122.448px; width: 103.108px; opacity: 0; box-sizing: border-box;"/></section></section><section style="margin: -3em 0px 0px; padding: 0px 10px 10px; border-color: rgb(151, 124, 66); border-style: dotted; border-width: 2px; border-radius: 0.3em; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 3.5em 0px 15px; text-align: left; line-height: 1.8; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box; line-height: normal;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box;">廖钒</span></strong></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box; line-height: normal;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box;">资深文化艺术讲师</span></strong></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box; line-height: normal;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box;">博物馆有得聊联合创始人</span></strong></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box; line-height: normal;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;"><br/></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box; line-height: normal;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;">做一件事情坚持超过15年的就该是真爱吧。从大学开始到现在，工作换了好几个，定期去博物馆一直没变过。</span><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box; line-height: normal;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box; line-height: normal;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;">她举办了近300场讲座。已为超过8万人讲解过国家博物馆15年来举办的50余个涵盖中外文明的展览。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box; line-height: normal;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box; line-height: normal;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box;">作为领队，她的准则是：讲之前，必须自己去过见过研究过。她自费考察了亚、欧、非20余个国家130多座城市的文化遗产、博物馆和古迹，直到现在，当她看到文艺复兴的雕塑作品，仍然心潮澎湃心动不已。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box; line-height: normal;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box;">“善于发现和抓住艺术背后的历史及人文线索，在不同文明多维度全方位的视角下观察文物，并用深入浅出的语言进行解读，给人以精神层面的共鸣和享受。”这是她的粉丝给她总结的一大特点，也是她的魅力“之一”。</span></p><p style="line-height: normal;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></span></p></section></section></section></section></section></section></section><p><br/></p><p style="white-space: normal;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box; text-align: center;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(151, 124, 66); font-size: 14px;"></span></strong></p><p><br/></p></section></section></section><p><br/></p><section style="font-size: medium; white-space: normal; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; width: 7em; height: 7em; display: inline-block; vertical-align: bottom; border-radius: 100%; border-width: 5px; border-style: solid; box-shadow: rgb(204, 204, 204) 0.707107px 0.707107px 2px; border-color: white; background-position: center center; background-repeat: no-repeat; background-size: cover; background-image: url(&#39;http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appkHUDlT435887/image/ueditor/70884000_1538622842.cn/mmbiz_jpg/icetjwgztmpga7447pixc967w8a9raqjvth4vs7mraovyanz7jwgkglzzybjaqud4xr3h4ia8yuovwffu9tkduibw/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&#39;);"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 103.108px; height: 103.108px; overflow: hidden; box-sizing: border-box;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appkHUDlT435887/image/ueditor/81542900_1538622842.cn/mmbiz_jpg/icetjwgztmpga7447pixc967w8a9raqjvth4vs7mraovyanz7jwgkglzzybjaqud4xr3h4ia8yuovwffu9tkduibw/640" width="100%" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; height: 116.788px; width: 103.108px; opacity: 0; box-sizing: border-box;"/></section></section><section style="margin: -3em 0px 0px; padding: 0px 10px 10px; border-color: rgb(151, 124, 66); border-style: dotted; border-width: 2px; border-radius: 0.3em; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 3.5em 0px 15px; text-align: left; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;">冯海啸</span></strong></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;">资深文化艺术讲师</span></strong><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;"><br/></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box; text-align: center;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;"><strong style="font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: medium; text-align: center; white-space: normal; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box;">博物馆有得聊联合创始人</span></strong></span></strong></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;">2004年至今，曾长期担任拍卖公司书画部、古籍善本部业务经理，鉴定并征集齐白石《群虾图》、程十发《长吉诗意兰香神女图》、吴湖帆旧藏清汪由敦、钱维城书画合璧册页、秦权清拓本、唐海兽葡萄纹铜镜、明宣德青花缠枝莲纹折沿盆、明嘉靖五十四年项氏万卷堂刊本《前四史论赞》、明万历刊本《乡贤区西屏集》、明万历三年刻本《史记钞》、民国徐乃昌影刻明寒山赵均小宛堂本《玉台新咏》等重要文物。撰写并发表了《宋刻天禄琳琅藏本〈后村居士集〉》、《万古词章楮墨传——谈民国藏书家徐乃昌覆刻的明寒山赵氏小宛堂本〈玉台新咏〉》等文章。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;">2003年起至今，讲解各类展览20余个，为观众服务千余小时，并撰写多个展览的讲解词。</span></p><p><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;"><br/></span></p></section></section></section></section></section></section></section><section style="font-size: medium; white-space: normal; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"></section></section><p><br/></p><p style="white-space: normal;"><br/></p><p><br/></p>

